%3Cbr%3E%5CnK2%20is%20among%20the%20toughest%20vertical%20steep%20climb%20among%20all%208000ers.%20It's%20a%20tough%20mountain%20with%20extreme%20and%20unpredictable%20weather%20conditions%2C%20while%20it's%20cleaning%20up%20is%20challenging%20and%20complex%20phenomenon%20particularly%20due%20to%20climatic%20conditions%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20pollution%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtfhiimJpdy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FtfhiimJpdy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Sajid%20Ali%20Sadpara%20(%40sajid_sadpara)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsajid_sadpara%2Fstatus%2F1687800079456083968%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20high-altitude%20tribute%20to%20Sajid's%20father%2C%20legendary%20climber%20Ali%20Sadpara%2C%20honouring%20the%20place%20where%20they%20bonded%20in%20nature%20and%20where%20his%20body%20remains%20after%20a%202021%20father-son%20expedition%20fell%20foul%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bsavage%20mountain%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20doing%20it%20from%20my%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20Sajid%20told%20an%20AFP%20team%20at%20K2%20Basecamp%2C%20where%205%2C150%20metres%20of%20elevation%20labours%20breathing%20and%20avalanches%20tremor%20off%20an%20amphitheatre%20of%20surrounding%20slopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20our%20mountain%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2025-year-old%20said%2C%20sizing%20up%20the%20task%20above.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20custodians.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%20Sajid%20was%20attempting%20a%20perilous%20winter%20ascent%20of%20K2%20with%20his%20father%20and%20two%20foreigners%20when%20illness%20forced%20him%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20men%20who%20carried%20on%20were%20later%20discovered%20dead%20below%20the%20%26quot%3Bbottleneck%26quot%3B%20--%20an%20overhang%20that%20looks%20like%20a%20frozen%20tidal%20wave%20on%20the%20final%20stretch%20before%20the%20summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESajid%20recovered%20his%20father's%20body%20and%20performed%20Islamic%20rites%20at%20an%20improvised%20grave%20near%20Camp%20Four%20--%20the%20last%20stopoff%20before%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20marked%20the%20spot%20with%20GPS%20coordinates%20before%20the%20mountain%20enveloped%20the%20remains%20at%20a%20height%20of%20more%20than%2023%20Eiffel%20Towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFaith%20in%20cleanliness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESajid%20bears%20that%20loss%20with%20soft-spoken%20grace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20voice%2C%20unbruised%20with%20emotion%2C%20is%20hard%20to%20make%20out%20in%20blaring%20Islamabad%20restaurants%20or%20the%20resort%20town%20of%20Skardu%20where%20a%20mural%20of%20his%20father%20looks%20on%20as%20expeditions%20jump%20off%20in%20growling%20jeeps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20nearby%20village%20of%20Choghoghrong%20--%20an%20oasis%20of%20golden%20cropland%20blotched%20with%20lavender%20bushes%20--%20it%20resonates%20as%20he%20recounts%20the%20uncommon%20appreciation%20of%20the%20natural%20world%20his%20father%20handed%20down%20while%20they%20worked%20the%20land%20between%20summit%20pushes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20simple%20life%20and%20this%20natural%20life%20we%20spent%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Sajid%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20whole%20world%20was%20my%20village.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20most%20connected%20with%20nature%20in%20this%20village%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20K2%20exerts%20a%20gravitational%20pull%3A%20a%20place%20of%20extreme%20risk%20but%20also%20the%20promise%20of%20absolute%20zen%20in%20the%20curious%2C%20adrenaline-addled%20climber's%20psyche.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20be%20on%20mountains%20just%20for%20mental%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20Sajid%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20see%20any%20rubbish%20the%20feeling%20is%20totally%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbbas%20Sadpara%20said%20%26quot%3BK2%20is%20no%20longer%20as%20beautiful%20as%20it%20once%20used%20to%20be.%20We%20have%20destroyed%20its%20beauty%20with%20our%20own%20hands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Sajid%20has%20climbed%20half%20the%208%2C000-metre%20peaks%20without%20supplemental%20oxygen%2C%20a%20daredevil%20undertaking%2C%20and%20holds%20no%20ill%20will%20towards%20those%20who%20jettison%20gear%20on%20the%20slopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20a%20summit%20you%20are%20totally%20exhausted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20main%20thing%20is%20survival.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20saying%20in%20Islam%20he%20is%20fond%20of%20recalling%3A%20%26quot%3BCleanliness%20is%20half%20of%20faith.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClimbing%20to%20the%20top%20is%20a%20different%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explains.%20%26quot%3BCleaning%20is%20something%20that%20you%20feel%20personally%20from%20the%20heart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETipping%20point%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20plastic%20waste%20was%20discovered%2011%20kilometres%20below%20the%20sea%20in%20the%20Mariana%20Trench%2C%20the%20deepest%20point%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20commercialised%20mountain%20tourism%20conveying%20growing%20numbers%20of%20tourists%20to%20the%20summit%2C%20Everest%20is%20also%20growing%20notorious%20for%20vast%20blemishes%20of%20trash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK2%20witnessed%20a%20record%20of%20some%20150%20summits%20last%20season%20prompting%20concern%20the%20same%20ironic%20dynamic%20--%20of%20climbers%20leaving%20trails%20of%20waste%20while%20pursuing%20the%20world's%20most%20untouched%20vistas%20--%20has%20crept%20into%20play%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20two%20mountains%20that%20the%20trash%20has%20been%20a%20problem%20and%20that's%20K2%20and%20Everest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Norwegian%20climber%20Kristin%20Harila%2C%2037%2C%20whose%20summit%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20peak%20last%20month%20sealed%20a%20record-quick%20ascent%20of%20all%208%2C000-metre%20mountains%20in%20three%20months%20and%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommercial%20companies%2C%20they%20take%20in%20more%20equipment%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20CKNP%20ecologist%20Yasir%20Abbas%2C%20who%20oversaw%20a%20campaign%20pulling%201%2C600%20kg%20of%20refuse%20off%20the%20mountain%20in%202022.%20%26quot%3BIf%20more%20people%20go%20to%20climb%20there%20will%20be%20more%20waste.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20goes%20up%20must%20come%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20are%20cleaning%20K2%20are%20risking%20their%20life%20for%20the%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20clean-up%20mission%20goes%20beyond%20the%20environmental%2C%20spilling%20into%20the%20code%20of%20fellowship%20climbers%20abide%20by%20at%20altitude%20--%20beyond%20the%20earthbound%20crutches%20of%20rescue%20services%20and%20emergency%20rooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECast-away%20ropes%20can%20mislead%20teams%20with%20minds%20clouded%20by%20altitude%20sickness%20towards%20oblivion.%20Abandoned%20tents%20force%20other%20campers%20out%20into%20more%20exposed%20spots%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20elements.%20Each%20tossed%20O2%20canister%20is%20another%20hefty%20hazard%20at%20the%20whim%20of%20gravity%20and%20wind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20my%20trash%20or%20your%20trash%2C%20it's%20our%20trash%2C%26quot%3B%20Harila%20told%20AFP%20in%20Islamabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%20in%20K2%20if%20there's%20some%20mistake%20you%20fall%20down.%20If%20you%20fall%20down%2C%20all%20the%20way%20you%20come%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mingma%20David%20Sherpa%2C%2033%2C%20who%20led%20a%20Nepalese%20team%20with%20the%20Nimsdai%20Foundation%20also%20clearing%20some%20200%20kilograms%20from%20K2%20before%20passing%20the%20baton%20to%20Sajid%20in%20mid-July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20before%20that%20moment%2C%20the%20young%20Sadpara%20sets%20eyes%20on%20the%20mountain%20after%