%2C%20The%20Moscow%20Times%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20last%20weekend's%20summit%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20where%20nations%20gathered%20to%20discuss%20Kyiv's%20plan%20to%20end%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20Russia%20is%20cutting%20an%20ever%20more%20isolated%20figure%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%20It%20seems%20to%20be%20striking%20a%20nerve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20summit%20in%20Jeddah%20representatives%20from%2040%20nations%20gathered%20to%20discuss%20Ukraine's%20proposals%20for%20ending%20the%20conflict.%20In%20a%20surprise%20move%20even%20Russia's%20staunchest%20international%20backer%2C%20China%2C%20sent%20a%20representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Chinese%20presence%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frift-grows-between-xi-putin-russia-refusal-ukraine-peace-deal-2023-8%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Ea%20growing%20rift%20between%20Beijing%20and%20Moscow%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20meanwhile%20Russia%20was%20not%20invited.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themoscowtimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F09%2Ftheyre-gossiping-without-us-saudi-hosted-peace-summit-underscores-kremlins-diplomatic-dilemma-a82103%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20comments%20to%20The%20Moscow%20Times%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20four%20former%20and%20current%20Kremlin%20officials%20familiar%20with%20Russia's%20diplomacy%20were%20troubled.%20Ukraine%20had%20managed%20to%20gather%20traditional%20Russian%20allies%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20not%20just%20its%20usual%20backers%20in%20the%20West%2C%20they%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20official%20said%20Ukraine%20was%20seeking%20to%20cut%20out%20Russia%20and%20get%20countries%20to%20rally%20behind%20its%20version%20of%20how%20to%20end%20the%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKyiv's%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20these%20countries%20if%20not%20allies%2C%20then%20partners.%20And%20then%20if%20a%20general%20consensus%20is%20reached%2C%20Ukraine%20will%20try%20to%20deepen%20it%20and%20raise%20more%20sensitive%20issues%20to%20build%20such%20a%20consensus%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20diplomat%20told%20the%20publication.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20high-ranking%20Russian%20diplomat%20also%20expressed%20concern%20to%20The%20Moscow%20Times%20about%20Russia's%20isolation%2C%20but%20added%20that%20Moscow's%20participation%20in%20discussions%20was%20necessary%20for%20ending%20the%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20we're%20not%20there%20is%20naturally%20unpleasant%20for%20us.%20As%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they're%20gossiping%20without%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20official%20said.%20He%20did%2C%20however%2C%20say%20that%20%26quot%3Byou%20cannot%20solve%26quot%3B%20the%20war%20without%20Russian%20input.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20have%20intensified%20their%20struggle%20to%20for%20diplomatic%20support%20for%20their%20versions%20of%20ending%20the%20war.%20Ukraine%20wants%20Russia%20to%20be%20totally%20expelled%20from%20its%20territory%2C%20while%20Russia%20wants%20to%20retain%20the%20portions%20of%20eastern%20and%20southern%20Ukraine%20it%20has%20conquered%20and%20claimed%20as%20its%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20focus%20is%20large%20economies%20outside%20the%20West%20%E2%80%94%20Brazil%2C%20India%2C%20China%20and%20South%20Africa%20%E2%80%94%20which%20alongside%20Russia%20are%20part%20of%20the%20so-called%20BRICS%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20non-Western%20powers%2C%20including%20India%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20have%20sat%20on%20the%20fence%20during%20the%20conflict%2C%20refusing%20to%20condemn%20Russia's%20war%20or%20impose%20sanctions%2C%20yet%20also%20not%20offering%20Russia%20explicit%20backing.%20Each%20of%20the%20BRICS%20nations%20apart%20from%20Russia%20sent%20representatives%20to%20Jeddah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20June%20summit%20convened%20by%20Ukraine%20in%20Denmark%20was%20more%20sparsely%20attended%2C%20suggesting%20there%20has%20been%20progress%20even%20in%20the%20few%20weeks%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20hopes%20to%20persuade%20nations%20by%20pointing%20to%20the%20devastating%20effect%20of%20Russia's%20war%20of%20the%20grain%20exports%20many%20countries%20depend%20on.%20Russia%20recently%20ended%20a%20truce%20with%20Ukraine%20to%20protect%20the%20grain%20trade%2C%20sparking%20widespread%20condemnation.%20In%20return%20Moscow%20has%20promised%20free%20grain%20to%20some%20African%20countries%20to%20offset%20the%20shortfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Jeddah%20conference%20shows%20that%20more%20countries%20are%20broadly%20receptive%20to%20Ukraine's%20plans%20to%20end%20the%20war%2C%20and%20are%20increasingly%20weary%20of%20Russia's%20intransigence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20meeting%20in%20Jeddah%2C%20inconclusive%20as%20it%20may%20have%20been%2C%20signals%20a%20continuing%20shift%20in%20Ukraine's%20favor%2C%20albeit%20at%20glacial%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Stefan%20Wolf%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobelynews.com%2Feurope%2Fsaudi-arabia-ukraine-talks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20professor%20of%20international%20security%20at%20Birmingham%20University%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20blog%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-angry-left-out-of-peace-talks-ukraine-gained-allies-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691665535000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d4bf6848a88f0019689916%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-angry-left-out-of-peace-talks-ukraine-gained-allies-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20talks%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20discuss%20Kyiv's%20Ukraine%20war%20peace%20plan%2C%20even%20Russia's%20ally%20China%20sent%20a%20delegate%2C%20infuriating%20Moscow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter