ed%20by%20the%20president%20based%20on%20advice%20from%20a%20committee%20comprising%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%20(CJI).%20That%20verdict%20was%20delivered%20in%20a%20batch%20of%20pleas%20seeking%20reforms%20in%20the%20process%20of%20appointing%20election%20commissioners%20since%20the%20executive%20enjoyed%20the%20power%20to%20make%20appointments%20in%20violation%20of%20Article%20324(2)%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20passing%20the%20order%2C%20the%20bench%20noted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20parliamentary%20law%20in%20place%20to%20lay%20down%20the%20selection%20procedure%20for%20election%20commissioners%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20its%20order%20was%20meant%20to%20fill%20the%20constitutional%20vacuum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%20Conditions%20of%20Service%20and%20Term%20of%20Office)%20Bill%2C%202023%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1689562359210340353%5C%22%3Eintroduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Thursday%20by%20Union%20law%20minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20even%20as%20opposition%20parties%20claimed%20that%20it%20would%20destroy%20the%20constitutional%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20Bill%20proposes%20to%20replace%20the%20CJI%20in%20the%20selection%20committee%20with%20a%20Union%20minister%20who%20is%20nominated%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20giving%20effective%20control%20of%20the%20appointment%20of%20election%20commissioners%20to%20the%20executive%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-law%2Fbill-election-commission-members-appointment-process-explained-8885676%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20parliament%20has%20the%20power%20to%20nullify%20the%20effect%20of%20a%20court%20ruling%20by%20addressing%20the%20concerns%20flagged%20in%20the%20judgment%2C%20the%20law%20cannot%20be%20contradictory%20to%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20arrangement%20prescribed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20specifically%20because%20the%20court%20noted%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98legislative%20vacuum%E2%80%99.%20Filling%20that%20vacuum%20is%20well%20within%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20since%20the%20court%20repeatedly%20emphasised%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20independent%20body%20to%20conduct%20elections%20in%20the%20judgment%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20LoP%20is%20outvoted%20even%20before%20the%20process%20begins%20may%20raise%20eyebrows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstitutional%20lawyer%20Gautam%20Bhatia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgautambhatia88%2Fstatus%2F1689561801266970624%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20SC%20verdict%20held%20that%20executive%20dominance%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20election%20commissioners%20was%20unconstitutional%20and%20that%20parliamentary%20law%20can%E2%80%99t%20breach%20that%20principle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Bill%2C%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20and%20other%20election%20commissioners%20shall%20be%20appointed%20by%20the%20president%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20a%20Selection%20Committee%20consisting%20of%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(a)%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20chairperson%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(b)%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%2C%20member%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(c)%20a%20Union%20cabinet%20minister%20to%20be%20nominated%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20adds%20that%20the%20search%20committee%20for%20election%20commissioners%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20the%20cabinet%20secretary%2C%20with%20two%20members%20who%20are%20not%20below%20the%20rank%20of%20secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20They%20will%20prepare%20a%20panel%20of%20five%20persons%20for%20consideration%20by%20the%20Selection%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20appointment%20of%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20Election%20Commissioners%20shall%20not%20be%20invalid%20merely%20by%20reason%20of%20any%20vacancy%20in%20or%20any%20defect%20in%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bill%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20sees%20bid%20to%20control%20poll%20panel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20Bill%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%20said%20that%20through%20the%20Bill%2C%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20make%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20a%20%E2%80%98Modi%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99.%20He%20decried%20the%20move%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Black%20Day%E2%80%99%20for%20Indian%20Democracy%20and%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbrazen%20assault%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20and%20bulldozing%20of%20the%20Constitutional%20independence%20of%20ECI%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CECI%20will%20now%20be%20among%20the%20last%20Constitutional%20institutions%20to%20fall%20at%20the%20altar%20of%20usurpation%20of%20power%20by%20any%20or%20all%20means%20by%20an%20autocrat%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20is%20an%20assault%20on%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Judiciary%20%26amp%3B%20people%E2%80%99s%20rights%20to%20elect%20their%20own%20government%20in%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frssurjewala%2Fstatus%2F1689584558835191808%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20proposed%20selection%20committee%20does%20not%20constitute%20a%20check%20and%20balance%20and%20will%20be%20an%20%E2%80%9Cempty%20formality%E2%80%9D%20since%20not%20a%20single%20cabinet%20minister%20will%20vote%20against%20the%20prime%20minister%20who%20nominated%20him%20or%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20leaders%20Saket%20Gokhale%20and%20Sushmita%20Dev%20said%20that%20it%20betrayed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20control%20an%20independent%20panel%20like%20the%20ECI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShocking.%20BJP%20is%20rigging%20the%202024%20election%20openly.%20Modi%20government%20has%20again%20brazenly%20trampled%20upon%20an%20SC%20judgment%20and%20is%20making%20the%20Election%20Commission%20its%20own%20bunch%20of%20stooges.%20In%20the%20(EC%20appointment)%20Bill%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20a%20Union%20Minister%20in%20the%20selection%20committee%20to%20appoint%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20the%20two%20Election%20Commissioners%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gokhale%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSaketGokhale%2Fstatus%2F1689535547310518273%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20its%20judgment%20had%20clearly%20noted%20that%20the%20Committee%20should%20be%20(A)%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20(B)%20the%20PM%20and%20(C)%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition.%20In%20the%20Bill%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20replaced%20the%20CJI%20with%20a%20union%20minister.%20Basically%20now%2C%20Modi%20and%20one%20minister%20will%20appoint%20the%20entire%20Election%20Commission.%20This%20is%20a%20clear%20step%20towards%20rigging%20the%202024%20elections%20after%20fear%20has%20been%20struck%20into%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20heart%20by%20the%20united%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDev%20said%20said%20that%20while%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20will%20be%20a%20member%20of%20the%20selection%20panel%2C%20they%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20outnumbered%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20a%20Union%20cabinet%20minister.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20yet%20another%20way%20to%20control%20an%20institution%20which%20must%20be%20independent.%E2%80%9D%20she%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20MLA%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20shows%20that%C2%A0Modi%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20trust%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAamAadmiParty%2Fstatus%2F1689583532291858432%5C%22%3Esaid%20at%20a%20press%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20%5BModi%5D%20took%20the%20CJI%20out%20of%20the%20panel%20and%20presented%20a%20Bill%20that%20now%20says%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20a%20minister%20chosen%20by%20the%20PM%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20will%20be%20appoint%20election%20commissioners.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20article%20was%20first%20published%20at%2012%3A30%20pm%20on%20August%2010%2C%202023%20and%20republished%20at%204%3A20%20pm%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691664646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2FElection_Commission_P1TI.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnew-bill-selection-of-election-commissioners%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20panel%20will%20be%20led%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20with%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20a%20Union%20cabinet%20minister%20as%20members.%20Opposition%20parties%20slammed%20the%20move%20as%20bulldozing%20of%20the%20constitutional%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnew-bill-selection-of-election-commissioners%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Hit%20Jamini-Kanwal%20Kiss%2C%20Shabana%20Azmi%20Found%20Old%20Pic%20With%20Dharmendra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShabana%20Azmi%20excavated%20her%20photo%20archive%20and%20struck%2024%20karat%20go