20government%20been%20ousted%20by%20a%20vote%20of%20no%20confidence%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Persian%20word%C2%A0%3Cem%3Etoshakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20its%20treasures%20would%20have%20remained%20elusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20dishonesty%20has%20been%20established%20beyond%20doubt%2C%E2%80%9D%20Judge%20Humayun%20Dilawar%20wrote%20in%20the%20ruling%2C%20sentencing%20Khan%20to%20three%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20misusing%20his%20premiership%20from%202018%20to%202022%20to%20buy%20and%20sell%20gifts%20from%20the%20Toshakhana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20(70)%20leader%20of%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20August%205%2C%20and%20through%20a%20notification%20issued%20on%20August%208%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20(ECP)%20disqualified%20him%20from%20holding%20public%20office%3A%20%E2%80%9CMr%20Imran%20Ahmed%20Khan%20Niazi%20is%20disqualified%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%20and%20is%20also%20de-notified%20as%20a%20returned%20candidate%20from%20constituency%20NA-45%20Kurram-I.%E2%80%9D%20(Subdivision%20of%20Kurram%20District%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20faces%20more%20than%20100%20cases%20of%20corruption%2C%20fraud%20and%20even%20assassination%20since%20his%20ouster%2C%20was%20previously%20detained%20in%20May.%20His%20arrest%20had%20set%20ablaze%20an%20intense%20political%20turmoil%2C%20with%20violent%20clashes%20between%20PTI%20supporters%20and%20police%2C%20and%20attacks%20on%20the%20habitually%20revered%20military%E2%80%99s%20installations.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20general%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20within%20the%20next%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20dissolving%20the%20National%20Assembly%20(Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20lower%20house)%20will%20begin%20from%20August%209%2C%20three%20days%20before%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20term%20ends.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20an%20early%20dissolution%2C%20the%20ECP%20is%20mandated%20to%20conduct%20general%20elections%20within%2090%20days.%20But%20the%20timely%20conduct%20of%20polls%20in%20Pakistan%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20dubitable%20undertaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20constitutional%20norms%20be%20followed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20a%20history%20of%20non-adherence%20to%20constitutional%20norms.%20The%20only%20democratic%20solution%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20protracted%20political%20and%20economic%20crises%20is%20for%20a%20freely%20elected%20civilian%20government%20with%20a%20fresh%20mandate.%20The%20composition%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20finalised.%20Once%20formed%2C%20will%20it%20be%20able%20to%20conduct%20polls%20within%20the%20constitutionally%20mandated%20period%20of%2090%20days%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%201%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Bureau%20of%20Statistics%20submitted%20to%20the%20Council%20of%20Common%20Interests%20(CCI)%20for%20approval%20of%20the%202023%20census.%20The%20ECP%20is%20required%20to%20carry%20out%20fresh%20delimitation%20of%20all%20the%20Assembly%20constituencies%20before%20the%20next%20general%20elections.%20The%20notification%20of%20the%202023%20census%20makes%20the%20delimitation%20process%20mandatory.%20Attendant%20to%20several%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20requirements%2C%20this%20will%20be%20time-consuming%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20situation%20wherein%20polls%20might%20not%20be%20held%20until%20early%202024.%20The%20interests%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(PPP)%20and%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20%E2%80%95%20Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20remain%20in%20deferring%20timely%20polls%2C%20lest%20the%20PTI%20make%20a%20strong%20showing.%20Their%20bet%20is%20that%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20disqualification%20and%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20elections%20would%20erode%20his%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fus-website-diplomatic-cable-imran-khan-foreign-conspiracy%5C%22%3EUS%20Site%20Publishes%20%E2%80%98Diplomatic%20Cable%E2%80%99%20at%20Heart%20of%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Foreign%20Conspiracy%E2%80%99%20Claim%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMilitary%20and%20political%20regression%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20in%20power%2C%20Khan%20found%20in%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa%2C%20then%20military%20chief%2C%20an%20ally%20for%20his%20campaign%20against%20corruption%2C%20primarily%20focused%20on%20punishing%20the%20Sharif%20(PML-N)%20and%20Bhutto%20(PPP)%20families.%20But%20the%20friendship%20soured%20because%20of%20bitter%20differences%20over%20issues%20such%20as%20who%20to%20appoint%20as%20the%20spymaster%2C%20and%20the%20extension%20of%20Bajwa%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%20During%20the%20May%209%20%E2%80%98protests%E2%80%99%20hundreds%20of%20Imran%20Khan%20supporters%20vandalised%20state%20buildings%2C%20including%20martyrs%E2%80%99%20monuments%20and%20sites%20such%20as%20the%20Army%20General%20Headquarters%20(GHQ)%20in%20Rawalpindi%20and%20the%20corps%20commander%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20military%20vowed%20to%20tighten%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnoose%20of%20law%E2%80%9D%20around%20%E2%80%9Cplanners%20and%20masterminds%20who%20mounted%20a%20hate-ripened%20and%20politically-driven%20rebellion%20against%20the%20state%20and%20state%20institutions.%E2%80%9D%20Imran%20Khan%20himself%20has%20been%20booked%20under%20the%20stringent%20Anti-Terrorism%20Act%2C%20over%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20army%20GHQ.%20Since%20the%20military%20crackdown%2C%20leaders%20have%20been%20deserting%20the%20PTI%20in%20droves%3B%2057%20of%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20party%20members%20announced%20they%20were%20forming%20their%20party%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20parliamentarians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20and%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20imprisonment%20have%20raised%20suspicions%20that%20the%20state%20was%20in%20a%20hurry%20to%20disqualify%20Khan%20from%20the%20upcoming%20general%20election.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EC%3C%2Fem%3Eould%20Khan%20still%20pose%20a%20risk%20to%20his%20rivals%20by%20supporting%20other%20candidates%20from%20behind%20bars%3F%C2%A0%20In%20a%20video%20recorded%20before%20his%20arrest%20and%20posted%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Khan%20again%20called%20on%20his%20supporters%20to%20take%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fallout%20with%20Khan%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20military%20sites%20and%20the%20subsequent%20military%20trials%20of%20civilians%2C%20all%20point%20towards%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20problematic%20military%20of%20Pakistan%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20letting%20its%20grip%20over%20politics%20ease.%20The%20nation%20is%20notorious%20for%20jailing%20former%20prime%20ministers%2C%20be%20it%20Hussain%20Shaheed%20Suhrawardy%2C%20Zulfikar%20Ali%20Bhutto%2C%20Benazir%20Bhutto%2C%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20and%20now%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20and%20avoiding%20any%20action%20against%20the%20military.%20Even%20as%20the%20five-year%20term%20of%20the%20National%20Assembly%20was%20coming%20to%20a%20close%2C%20legislation%20amending%20the%20Official%20Secrets%20Act%20bill%2C%20which%20amplifies%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI)%2C%20was%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20interesting%20twist%3A%20will%20self-exiled%2C%20three-time%20former%20PM%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ede%20facto%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0head%20of%20PML-N%2C%20return%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20lead%20its%20election%20campaign%3F%20In%20late%20June%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20National%20Assembly%20passed%20a%20bill%20to%20limit%20the%20lifetime%20disqualification%20of%20lawmakers%20to%20five%20years%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20return%20of%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20from%20London%20to%20resume%20active%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20popular%20demand%20for%20general%20elections%20is%20gaining%20momentum%20in%20Pakistan.%20Further%20delaying%20of%20elections%20carries%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20political%20uncertainty.%20A%20day%20ago%2C%20PM%20Sharif%20recommended%20the%20dissolution%20of%20parliament.%20Amidst%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20military%20institutionalisation%2C%20economic%20chaos%2C%20soaring%20inflation%2C%20an%20acute%20shortage%20of%20gas%20and%20electricity%20and%20a%20general%20state%20of%20despair%2C%20outgoing%20PM%20Sharif%20has%20announced%20the%20auction%20of%20Toshakhana%20gifts%2C%20the%20proceeds%20of%20which%20would%20be%20spent%20on%20welfare%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVaishali%20Basu%20Sharma%20is%20an%20analyst%20of%20strategic%20and%20economic%20affairs.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691663747000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F07221444%2FScreenshot-2023-06-07-at-10.13.10-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-election-military-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fallout%20with%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20military%20sites%20and%20the%20subsequent%20military%20trials%20of%20civilians%2C%20all%20point%20towards%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20such%20plan%20is%20afoot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-election-military-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tributes%20to%20British%20surgeon%20Kar%20Hao%20Teoh%20killed%20in%20South%20Af