nk%5C%22%3Edevastating%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ppic.org%2Fblog%2Fhomeless-populations-are-rising-around-california%2F%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22d893b5453fcd41bd44bbc332c01abbd3%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ppic.org%2Fblog%2Fhomeless-populations-are-rising-around-california%2F%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20homelessness%20problem%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20concerning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfchronicle.com%2Fbayarea%2Farticle%2Frobberies-san-francisco-18185651.php%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWhile%2520San%2520Francisco%2520isn%2527t%2Cchanges%2520to%2520city%2520life%2520linger.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshift%20in%20crime%20patterns%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSan%20Francisco%20used%20to%20have%20the%20lowest%20office%20vacancy%20in%20the%20US%20of%20any%20major%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexander%20Quinn%2C%20director%20of%20research%20at%20real%20estate%20company%20Jones%20Lang%20LaSalle%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcbayarea.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fsan-francisco-office-vacancy%2F3204043%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVacancy%20is%20now%20at%20around%2028%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20would%20put%20it%20at%20the%20highest%20of%20any%20major%20market%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20was%20the%20major%20culprit%20behind%20this%20decline%2C%20Nick%20Romito%20%E2%80%93%20CEO%20of%20commercial%20real%20estate%20leasing%20and%20asset%20management%20platform%20VTS%20%E2%80%93%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSan%20Francisco%20was%20a%20white-hot%20market%20driven%20mostly%20by%20technology.%20To%20go%20from%20that%20to%20quite%20literally%20the%20worst%20market%20in%20the%20country%20over%20the%20course%20of%20two%20years%20is%20kind%20of%20unprecedented%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20are%20starting%20to%20turn%20around%20for%20San%20Francisco's%20faltering%20commercial%20real%20estate%20market%20and%20the%20city%20may%20have%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20thank%20for%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20excitement%20around%20generative%20AI%20since%20the%20launch%20of%20Open%20AI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%20has%20spurred%20a%20flood%20of%20investor%20interest%20in%20major%20companies%20and%20start-ups%20alike.%20Now%2C%20some%20appear%20to%20be%20hunting%20for%20more%20office%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vts.com%2Fnews%2Fdemand-for-office-space-remains-muted-but-stable-as-employers-take-a-wait-and-see-approach%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20from%20VTS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20San%20Francisco%20saw%20a%20recent%20boom%20in%20demand%2C%20experiencing%20a%2010.2%25%20demand%20increase%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20quarter.%20Romito%20links%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20increase%20to%20the%20recent%20AI%20boom.%20OpenAI%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20headquartered%20in%20San%20Francisco's%20Mission%20District.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20certainly%20enough%20capital%20to%20cause%20a%20nice%20leap%20in%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20estimated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsfstandard.com%2F2023%2F07%2F10%2Fsan-francisco-companies-got-half-the-worlds-ai-funding-so-far-this-year%2F%3Ftaid%3D64c9c7a2d53f42000199082b%26utm_campaign%3Dtrueanthem%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2411%20billion%20worth%20of%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%20poured%20into%20San%20Francisco-based%20AI%20companies%20this%20year.%20The%20figure%20accounts%20for%20nearly%20half%20of%20all%20funding%20for%20AI%20startups%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPretty%20much%20all%20the%20data%20points%20to%20this%20demand%20coming%20from%20companies%20that%20are%20tangentially%20connected%20to%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Romito%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20perhaps%20unsurprising%20that%20AI%20companies%20seem%20to%20have%20San%20Francisco%20in%20their%20sights.%20The%20city%20is%20home%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fai-startups-bringing-dollars-lean-workforces-ailing-san-francisco-2023-07-13%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEleven%2520of%2520the%2520country%2527s%2520top%2Cfrom%2520venture%2520capital%2520firm%2520NFX.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E11%20of%20the%20top-funded%20companies%20in%20the%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20VC%20firm%20NFX%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20with%20Insider%20by%20San%20Francisco's%20Office%20of%20Economic%20and%20Workforce%20Development.%20These%20companies%20include%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20Adept%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpecifically%20in%20San%20Francisco%20we%20are%20at%20the%20epicenter%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20Quinn%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20result%20that's%20pushing%20us%20into%20growth%20in%20that%20sector%20and%20we%20are%20seeing%20growing%20requirements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuinn%20said%20JLL%20had%2010%20AI%20clients%20eyeing%20around%20750%2C000%20to%20one%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20San%20Francisco%20real%20estate.%20One%20AI%20company%2C%20Hive%2C%20recently%20announced%20it%20was%20subleasing%20three%20floors%20of%20a%20downtown%20San%20Francisco%20office%20%E2%80%94%20taking%20over%20space%20previously%20occupied%20by%20software%20company%20Okta%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-06-30%2Fartificial-intellige