%2Fwww.governor.ny.gov%2Fprograms%2Fnew-york-housing-compact%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Housing%20Compact%3C%2Fa%3E%20aimed%20to%20build%20800%2C000%20new%20units%2C%20with%20new%20housing%20concentrated%20near%20transit%20stations%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20would%20have%20extended%20the%20421-a%20tax%20break%2C%20which%20has%20encouraged%20significant%20housing%20development.%20But%20the%20effort%20failed%20after%20Republican%20and%20centrist%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20opposed%20it.%20A%20big%20portion%20of%20the%20opposition%20to%20the%20legislation%20came%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-new-york-suburbs-losing-minds-hochul-plan-increase-housing-2023-4%5C%22%3Esuburban%20areas%20around%20New%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20didn't%20want%20to%20see%20more%20density%20in%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20governor's%20office%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F18%2Fnyregion%2Fhousing-crisis-421a-hochul.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20executive%20actions%3C%2Fa%3E%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20housing%20construction%20that%20include%20tax%20incentives%20for%20developers%20and%20an%20effort%20to%20allow%20new%20housing%20on%20state-owned%20land.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Manhattan%20that's%20been%20building%20very%20little%20housing.%20The%20suburbs%20of%20New%20York%20City%20have%20also%20approved%20and%20constructed%20very%20few%20new%20units%20in%20recent%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20town%20of%20Munsey%20Park%20in%20Nassau%20County%20on%20Long%20Island%20permitted%20a%20total%20of%20four%20new%20single-family%20homes%20between%20between%202010%20and%202021%2C%20Politico%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnewsletters%2Fweekly-new-york-real-estate-infrastructure%2F2023%2F08%2F07%2Fgoing-town-by-town-on-the-paltry-housing-