0of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20alleged%20flying%20kiss%20in%20Parliament%20after%20his%20speech%20during%20the%20no-confidence%20debate%20yesterday.%20The%20minister%20had%20expressed%20outrage%20and%20said%20that%20the%20House%20had%20never%20witnessed%20such%20an%20%26quot%3Bindecent%20act%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20BJP%20MPs%20had%20also%20demanded%20action%20and%20complained%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20insulted%20women%20with%20his%20%26quot%3Bindecent%20gesture%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20BJP%20MP%20and%20outgoing%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20BJP%20MP%20was%20accused%20of%20harassment%20and%20molestation%20by%20our%20champion%20wrestlers%2C%20we%20did%20not%20hear%20one%20word%20out%20of%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20minister%20and%20now%20she%20is%20talking%20about%20some%20flying%20kiss.%20Where%20are%20your%20priorities%2C%20madam%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Irani%20had%20said%20yesterday%2C%20%26quot%3BNever%20before%20has%20the%20misogynistic%20behaviour%20of%20a%20man%20been%20so%20visible%20in%20parliament.%20When%20the%20House%20of%20the%20people%20-%20where%20laws%20are%20made%20to%20protect%20the%20dignity%20of%20women%20-%20during%20the%20course%20of%20a%20session%20stands%20witness%20to%20a%20man's%20misogyny%2C%20my%20question%20is%20should%20he%20be%20brought%20to%20task%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20countered%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20was%20gesturing%20towards%20slogan-shouting%20BJP%20MPs.%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20gestured%20towards%20the%20treasury%20benches%20as%20he%20was%20leaving%20with%20a%20flying%20kiss%20as%20he%20had%20called%20them%20brothers%20and%20sisters.%20He%20did%20not%20direct%20it%20towards%20any%20particular%20minister%20or%20MP%2C%20and%20not%20at%20all%20towards%20Smriti%20Irani%2