ars%20after%20his%20retirement%2C%20the%20charismatic%20lead%20actor%20assumes%20a%20circumspect%2C%20unflashy%20persona%20who%20does%20not%20swing%20into%20'action'%20until%20he%20is%20left%20with%20no%20other%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protagonist%2C%20former%20Tihar%20Jail%20warden%20%26quot%3BTiger'%20Muthuvel%20Pandian%2C%20who%20once%20had%20prisoners%20live%20in%20dread%20of%20his%20whims%2C%20has%20hung%20up%20his%20boots.%20He%20now%20focuses%20on%20the%20career%20of%20his%20police%20officer-son%2C%20Arjun%20(Vasantha%20Ravi)%2C%20who%20he%20has%20raised%20to%20be%20as%20honest%20and%20fearless%20as%20he%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuthu%20is%20a%20paragon%20of%20probity%2C%20a%20dutiful%20family%20man%20and%2C%20when%20push%20comes%20to%20shove%2C%20an%20unvanquishable%20thalaivar%20who%20brooks%20no%20trifling%20with%20things%20and%20people%20he%20holds%20dear.%20His%20transition%20from%20a%20seemingly%20docile%20grandfather%20going%20about%20his%20domestic%20chores%20to%20a%20vengeful%20executioner%20who%20wields%20a%20scimitar%20to%20deadly%20effect%2C%20does%20not%20take%20place%20until%20the%20film%20is%20well%20into%20its%20first%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20the%20process%20attains%20completion%2C%20the%20Anirudh%20Ravichander%20musical%2C%20which%20has%20only%20one%20lip-synched%20number%20performed%20on%20screen%20by%20Tamannaah%20Bhatia%2C%20comes%20up%20with%20something%20akin%20to%20a%20theme%20song%20that%20celebrates%20the%20superstar's%20mass%20appeal%20across%20generations.%20The%20song%20erases%20the%20gulf%20between%20the%20fictional%20world%20of%20Muthuvel%20Pandian%20and%20the%20real%20universe%20that%20Rajinikanth%20has%20lorded%20over%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJailer%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20Tamil%20film%2C%20but%20given%20the%20cameos%20by%20Mohanlal%2C%20Jackie%20Shroff%2C%20Shiva%20Rajkumar%20and%20Makarand%20Deshpande%2C%20several%20other%20languages%20are%20spoken%20by%20the%20actors%2C%20include%20Rajinikanth%20-%20Malayalam%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Telugu%20and%20Hindi.%20It%20is%20clearly%20and%20intrinsically%20a%20movie%20aimed%20at%20a%20pan-Indian%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20might%20argue%20that%20most%20Rajinikanth%20films%20are%20designed%20for%20nationwide%20consumption%20but%20Jailer%20isn't%20just%20another%20Tamil-language%20film%20meant%20to%20be%20distributed%20in%20the%20form%20of%20dubbed%20versions.%20It%20is%20best%20to%20see%20its%20original%20version%20with%20subtitles%20because%20only%20then%20will%20one%20get%20a%20sense%20what%20the%20film%20is%20trying%20to%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20that%20the%20Rajinikanth%20aura%20is%20in%20need%20of%20any%20sort%20of%20resurrection.%20What%20Jailer%20does%20is%20project%20him%20for%20what%20he%20is%20and%20has%20always%20aspired%20to%20be%20-%20a%20star%20for%20all%20seasons%20and%20all%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20the%20film%20serve%20its%20purpose%3F%20The%20first%20half%20of%20%3Cem%3EJailer%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20engaging%20for%20the%20most%20part.%20Its%20second%20half%20isn't%20half%20as%20riveting.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20sluggish%20and%20all%20over%20the%20place%20notwithstanding%20a%20couple%20of%20climactic%20twists%20that%20pack%20a%20reasonable%20punch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20scene%20in%20the%20second%20half%2C%20Muthu%20confronts%20a%20film%20director%20named%20Balu%20and%20exhorts%20him%20not%20to%20foist%20garbage%20on%20the%20audience%20in%20the%20name%20of%20commercial%20cinema.%20Give%20them%20clean%20family%20entertainment%2C%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20family%20all%20right%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Jailer%2C%20but%20does%20the%20film%20live%20up%20to%20Muthu's%20prescription.%20It%20doesn't.%20For%20one%2C%20there%20is%20way%20too%20much%20gore%20in%20the%20film%20for%20it%20to%20be%20suitable%20for%20all%20age%20groups.%20Not%20all%20of%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20film%20is%20perpetrated%20by%20the%20villain%20who%20dunks%20gang%20members%20who%20goof%20up%20into%20sulphuric%20acid%20vats.%20The%20hero%2C%20too%2C%20is%20just%20as%20ruthless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FY5BeWdODPqo%3Fsi%3D7YsT8Kn9wcznwA2d%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20sequence%2C%20Muthu%20decapitates%20a%20goon%20and%20then%20proceeds%20to%20regret%20that%20the%20headless%20man%20can%20longer%20fulfil%20his%20desire%20to%20see%20Muthu's%20angry%20face.%20The%20film%20plays%20out%20in%20a%20hyper%20masculine%20world%20where%20the%20women%20do%20not%20so%20much%20as%20play%20second%20fiddle.%20They%20are%20allowed%20no%20play%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuthu%20treats%20his%20wife%20and%20daughter-in-law%20as%20liabilities%20incapable%20of%20fending%20for%20themselves.%20So%2C%20every%20time%20the%20bad%20guy%20threatens%20to%20harm%20his%20family%2C%20the%20patriarch%20has%20to%20step%20in%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20to%20protect%20them.%20The%20only%20other%20woman%20in%20the%20film%20who%20has%20a%20few%20scenes%20is%20a%20movie%20actress%20played%20by%20Tamannaah.%20She%20is%20plied%20with%20gifts%20by%20two%20men%20-%20a%20film%20director%20and%20a%20male%20star%2C%20neither%20of%20whom%20think%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20ask%20her%20what%20she%20wants.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20film%20begins%2C%20Muthuvel%20Pandian%20(Rajinikanth)%20leads%20a%20quiet%20life%20with%20his%20wife%20Vijaya%20(Ramya%20Krishnan)%2C%20daughter-in-law%20Shwetha%20(Mirna%20Menon)%20and%20grandson.%20He%20is%20happy%20to%20shop%20for%20vegetables%2C%20help%20his%20grandson%20shoot%20insta%20reels%2C%20and%20indulge%20in%20prickly%20banter%20with%20a%20Bharathiyar-quoting%20taxi%20driver%20(Yogi%20Babu)%20who%20keeps%20threatening%20to%20run%20him%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20son%2C%20an%20assistant%20commissioner%20of%20police%2C%20is%20on%20the%20trail%20of%20a%20gang%20of%20antique%20smugglers%20led%20by%20the%20vicious%20Varma%20(Vinayakan).%20One%20fine%20day%2C%20the%20officer%20goes%20missing.%20Word%20gets%20around%20that%20he%20is%20dead.%20Muthu's%20wife%20blames%20him%20for%20the%20fate%20that%20has%20befallen%20Arjun.%20It%20is%20you%20who%20conditioned%20him%20to%20be%20so%20upright%20and%20uncompromising%2C%20she%20laments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Btiger%26quot%3B%20dormant%20in%20the%20guilt-ridden%20Muthu%20resurfaces.%20Roping%20in%20the%20cabbie%20who%20needles%20him%20needlessly%2C%20the%20ex-jailer%20kills%20the%20man%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20murdered%20his%20son.%20The%20kill%20takes%20place%20off-screen%2C%20a%20sign%20that%20Jailer%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20Rajinikanth%20film%20with%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20subsequent%20action%20scenes%2C%20however%2C%20Muthu%20uses%20sharp-edged%20weapons%20and%20guns%20to%20dispatch%20the%20hoodlums%20to%20their%20doom%20but%20in%20most%20other%20sequences%20he%20relies%20on%20a%20group%20of%20snipers%20provided%20to%20him%20by%20his%20friend%20from%20Mandya%2C%20Narasimha%20(Shiva%20Rajkumar).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Cem%3EKabali%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Rajinikanth's%20sphere%20of%20action%20was%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20in%20Kaala%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20slum%20and%20in%20his%20last%20release%20Annaatthe%20(2021)%2C%20circumstances%20saw%20him%20move%20to%20Kolkata.%20In%20%3Cem%3EJailer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20operates%20all%20across%20India%20because%20he%20has%20friends%20everywhere.%20That%20is%20where%20Mohanlal%20and%20Jackie%20Shroff%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20stars%20do%20their%20bit%20and%20move%20on.%20It%20is%20left%20to%20Rajinikanth%20to%20shoulder%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20erratic%20script.%20Playing%20an%20age-appropriate%20character%2C%20the%20septuagenarian%20star%20pulls%20his%20weight%20all