ints%20their%20house%20a%20specific%20colour%20to%20game%20the%20system%20and%20impress%20the%20Google%20Street%20View%20Car%2C%26quot%3B%20Ratti%20wrote.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-real-estate-prices-home-values-predictions-retirement-mit-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691662501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d3e31fec14ba0019f38576%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-real-estate-prices-home-values-predictions-retirement-mit-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MIT%20used%20an%20AI%20bot%20to%20make%20what%20researchers%20called%20%26quot%3Bvery%20accurate%26quot%3B%20predictions%20for%20how%20home%20prices%20would%20change%20over%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-real-estate-prices-home-values-predictions-retirement-mit-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20India%20Hockey%20Coach's%20Take%20%5C%22Structured%5C%22%20Dig%20At%20Pakistan%20After%204-0%20Win%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Pakistan%20hockey%20coach%20Muhammad%20Saqlain%20said%20that%20India%20were%20not%20playing%20a%20'structural%20game'%20at%20the%20Asian%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20his%20team%20were%20dealt%20a%204-0%20loss%20by%20the%20hosts%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20not%20playing%20structural%20hockey%2C%20but%20Pakistan%20is.%20India%20is%20simply%20playing%20over%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20Saqlain%20said%20during%20pre-match%20media%20conference.%20%26quot%3BStructural%20hockey%20is%20played%20by%20Korea%20and%20Japan.%20India%20has%20been%20playing%20behind%20the%20ball%20mostly%20and%20relying%20mainly%20on%20counter-attacking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20after%20the%20win%2C%20India%20head%20coach%20Craig%20Fulton%20hailed%20his%20side's%20%26quot%3Bstructured%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%26quot%3B%20game%20in%20the%204-0%20thrashing%20of%20arch-rivals%20Pakistan%20in%20their%20Asian%20Champions%20Trophy%20hockey%20match%20and%20he's%20looking%20for%20his%20players%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20same%20vein%20in%20the%20semifinal%20against%20Japan.%20India's%20comprehensive%204-0%20win%20in%20their%20last%20round-robin%20league%20match%20on%20Wednesday%20knocked%20Pakistan%20out%20of%20the%20tournament.%20Unbeaten%20India%20topped%20the%20league%20table%20with%20four%20wins%20and%20a%20draw%20and%20play%20Japan%20in%20the%20semifinals%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20play%20a%20good-structured%20game.%20We%20did%20miss%20a%20few%20chances%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20but%20we%20did%20well%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20Fulton%20said%20during%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20some%20good%20consistency%20in%20each%20quarter%2C%20which%20we%20did%20the%20same%20during%20the%20Japan%20game%20(on%20August%204%20which%20ended%20in%201-1%20draw).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20sneaked%20into%20the%20semifinals%20ahead%20of%20Pakistan%20on%20better%20goal%20difference%2C%20though%20the%20two%20sides%20collected%20five%20points%20each.%20Japan%20had%20minus%20two%20goal%20difference%20as%20against%20minus%20five%20of%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20third-placed%20Korea%20also%20secured%20five%20points%20but%20they%20have%20a%20goal%20difference%20of%20minus%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20had%20more%20penetration%20into%20the%20circle%20in%20each%20quarter%20than%20Japan.%20So%2C%20it%20will%20be%20about%20maintaining%20consistency%20and%20not%20doing%20it%20just%20one%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Fulton%20said%20about%20the%20semifinal%20against%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20were%20disallowed%20a%20goal%20after%20video%20referral%20early%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20ball%20had%20hit%20a%20player's%20body%20before%20he%20scored.%20Pakistan%20coach%20Muhammad%20Saqlain%20later%20complained%20that%20India's%20first%20penalty%20corner%20from%20which%20the%20hosts%20took%201-0%20lead%20off%20captain%20Harmanpreet%20Singh's%20drag-flick%20was%20wrongly%20awarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20conceded%20through%20India's%20first%20penalty%20corner%2C%20but%20it%20came%20off%20the%20hand.%20The%20second%20umpire%20did%20inform%20that%20it%20wasn't%20a%20PC%2C%20but%20the%20other%20umpire%20did%20not%20hear%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Saqlain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20the%20referral%20in%20the%20process.%20Such%20mistakes%20cannot%20happen%20at%20this%20level%2C%20especially%20when%20we%20are%20playing%20against%20the%20top%20sides%20in%20the%20world.%20So%2C%20the%20standard%20of%20umpiring%20needs%20improvement%2C%20which%20has%20been%20inconsistent%20in%20the%20event%20throughout%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20umpiring%20decisions%20in%20the%20match%2C%20Fulton%20played%20with%20a%20straight%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20video%20referrals%20are%20for.%20It%20(Pakistan's%20disallowed%20goal)%20was%20scored%20off%20the%20body.%20But%20there%20are%20some%20goals%20that%20umpires%20can't%20disallow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20they%20(Pakistan)%20played%20well.%20They%20had%20chances%2C%20but%20we%20defended%20well%20and%20got%20the%20goals%20counted%20at%20the%20right%20time.%26quot%3B%20Jugraj%20Singh%20scored%20India's%20third%20goal%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20off%20a%20penalty%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20decision-making%20process%20regarding%20Jugraj%20being%20asked%20to%20take%20the%20penalty%20croner%2C%20Fulton%20said%20it%20was%20planned%20and%20%26quot%3Bit%20all%20happened%20behind%20the%20scenes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20study%20on%20it.%20I%20can't%20tell%20you%20everything%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20he%20(Jugraj)%20has%20to%20execute%20it.%20So%2C%20he%20deserves%20all%20the%20credit%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20warm-up%2C%20I%20saw%20Jugraj%20flick%20one%20good%2C%20and%20I%20told%20him%2C%20'When%20I%20call%20you%20to%20flick%2C%20that's%20how%20you%20do%20it'.%20Ultimately%2C%20it%20worked.%20But%2C%20sometimes%20it%20works%2C%20and%20sometimes%20it%20doesn't.%20I'm%20glad%20it%20worked%20today.%26quot%3B%20Captain%20Harmanpreet%20Singh%20struck%20twice%20from%20penalty%20corners%20to%20play%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20my%20drag-flick%20is%20concerned%2C%20even%20if%20I%20miss%20out%20on%20one%20or%20two%20shots%2C%20I%20know%20I%20will%20get%20more%20opportunities%2C%20and%20my%20focus%20is%20on%20trying%20to%20get%20those%20converted.%26quot%3B%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20Saqlain%20had%20said%20that%20India%20were%20not%20playing%20structured%20hockey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Saqlain's%20pre-match%20comments%2C%20Harmanpreet%20simply%20said%20that%20India%20would%20be%20looking%20to%20better%20the%20structure%20if%20that%20indeed%20was%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20are%20winning%20without%20playing%20in%20a%20structure%2C%20then%20we%20will%20try%20to%20better%20our%20structure.%20He%20has%20given%20us%20a%20good%20lesson%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20decision-making%20process%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20Harmanpreet%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20discussed%20things%20during%20every%20team%20meeting.%20Our%20graph%20has%20been%20going%20up.%20We%20are%20being%20told%20which%20area%20we%20are%20improving%2C%20and%20how%20to%20stay%20mentally%20strong%20and%20build%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20always%20discussed%20before%20every%20match%20that%20we%20must%20not%20forget%20our%20original%20game.%20There%20will%20be%20pressure%20from%20the%20crowd.%20But%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20keep%20your%20responsibility%20and%20stay%20focused.%20We%20did%20well%20today%20(Wednesday)%20but%20could%20have%20done%20even%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMidfielder%20Mandeep%20Singh%20displayed%20great%20composure%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Fulton%20explained%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20play%20in%20his%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMandeep's%20position%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20play%20in%20the%20side%20since%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20defending%20and%20attacking.%20But%20he%20is%20a%20seasoned%20professional%20and%20he%20knows%20how%20to%20play%20in%20it%2C%20and%20he%20has%20done%20it%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20He's%20bringing%20his%20experience%20into%20play%2C%20and%20he's%20doing%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691662320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F6fbj9oao_hockey-india_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fhockey%2Fdid-india-hockey-coach-craig-fulton-take-veiled-structured-dig-at-pakistan-after-4-0-thrashing-4285346%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20comprehensive%204-0%20win%20in%20their%20last%20round-robin%20league%20match%20on%20Wednesday%20knocked%20Pakistan%20out%20of%20the%20tournament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fhockey%2Fdid-india-hockey-coach-craig-fulton-take-veiled-structured-dig-at-pakistan-after-4-0-thrashing-4285346%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fhockey%2Fdid-india-hockey-coach-craig-fulton-take-veiled-structured-dig-at-pakistan-after-4-0-thrashing-4285346%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22http