0independence%20from%20British%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%20core%20goal%2C%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20had%20huge%20dimensions%20covering%20freedom%20of%20press%20and%20democracy%20which%20are%20in%20serious%20danger%20in%20our%20country%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20before%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20was%20launched%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Congress%20Committee%20on%20August%207%2C%201942%2C%20very%20presciently%20said%20that%20apart%20from%20helping%20India%20attain%20freedom%2C%20the%20historic%20movement%20would%20usher%20in%20democracy%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20raised%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98Quit%20India%E2%80%99%20the%20people%20in%20India%20who%20were%20then%20feeling%20despondent%20felt%20I%20had%20placed%20before%20them%20a%20new%20thing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asserted%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20real%20freedom%20you%20will%20have%20to%20come%20together%20and%20such%20coming%20together%20will%20create%20true%20democracy%20%E2%80%93democracy%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20has%20not%20been%20so%20far%20witnessed%2C%20nor%20have%20there%20been%20any%20attempts%20made%20for%20such%20type%20of%20true%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20he%20had%20read%20a%20good%20deal%20about%20the%20French%20Revolution%20and%20went%20through%20Thomas%20Carlyle%E2%80%99s%20work%20in%20jail.%20He%20added%20that%20Pandit%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20had%20explained%20to%20him%20all%20about%20the%20Russian%20revolution%20as%20well.%20He%20held%20that%20though%20those%20were%20fights%20for%20the%20people%2C%20they%20were%20not%20fights%20for%20the%20kind%20of%20real%20democracy%20which%20he%20envisaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmeans%20every%20man%20is%20his%20own%20master%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fquit-india-movement-narendra-modi-gandhi-netaji%5C%22%3ERemembering%20Those%20Who%20Opposed%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20%E2%80%93%20And%20Who%20Didn%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20read%20sufficient%20history%20and%20I%20did%20not%20see%20such%20an%20experiment%20on%20so%20large%20a%20scale%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20democracy%20by%20non-violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20you%20understand%20these%20things%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20will%20forget%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Muslims%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnity%20under%20attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20tragic%20that%20as%20we%20celebrate%20the%20anniversary%20of%20that%20epoch%20making%20Movement%2C%20India%20is%20getting%20polarised%20by%20the%20pronouncement%20of%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20regime%20of%20our%20country.%20These%20leaders%20employ%20binary-based%20Hindu-Muslim%20narratives%20to%20divide%20people%20along%20religious%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20distinctions%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20which%20Gandhi%20hoped%20would%20be%20eliminated%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20democracy%20following%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20have%20been%20accentuated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20communal%20and%20sinister%20happenings%20in%20Nuh%20in%20Haryana%20manifested%20in%20the%20form%20of%20targeted%20attack%20on%20Muslims%20by%20Hindutva%20forces.%20The%20latter%20organised%20a%20religious%20procession%20predominantly%20through%20Muslim%20dominated%20areas%20and%20used%20provocative%20slogans%20against%20them.%20Hatred%20was%20carefully%20cultivated%20against%20Muslims%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20be%20subjected%20to%20spiralling%20violence%20and%20exclusion%20on%20account%20of%20their%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brutal%20employment%20of%20bulldozers%20by%20th