rsis%20or%20those%20whose%20names%20were%20never%20heard%20within%20Congress%20circles%20would%20be%20entrusted%20with%20the%20power%20to%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20it%20clear%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20not%20feel%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20those%20who%20fought%20for%20it%20were%20Hindus%20and%20the%20number%20of%20Muslims%20and%20Parsis%20in%20the%20fight%20was%20small.%E2%80%9D%20Advocating%20for%20a%20change%20of%20mentality%20after%20getting%20freedom%2C%20he%20emphasised%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20the%20slightest%20communal%20taint%20in%20your%20minds%2C%20keep%20off%20the%20struggle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20earnest%20pleadings%20that%20elimination%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%20differences%20and%20removal%20of%20the%20slightest%20communal%20taint%20formed%20the%20backdrop%20against%20which%20Quit%20India%20was%20launched.%20Those%20defining%20attributes%20are%20now%20being%20annihilated%20by%20those%20wielding%20state%20apparatus%20in%20India%20and%20they%2C%20through%20their%20calibrated%20measures%2C%20are%20spelling%20ruin%20to%20those%20very%20founding%20ideals%20of%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutlining%20the%20core%20objective%20of%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20as%20freedom%20of%20our%20country%20from%20British%20rule%20Gandhi%20had%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCommunal%20unity%20must%20follow%20as%20day%20follows%20night%20when%20the%20night%20of%20foreign%20domination%20is%20gone%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-violence-rpf-constables-murder-new-phase-anti-muslim-hate%5C%22%3ENuh%20Violence%20and%20RPF%20Constable%E2%80%99s%20Murder%20Spree%20Reveal%20a%20New%20Phase%20of%20Anti-Muslim%20Hate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20divisiveness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aforementioned%20s