ty%20found%20that%20those%20who%20work%20from%20home%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20be%20constrained%20by%20other%20responsibilities%2C%20like%20childcare%20or%20household%20duties.%3Cp%3EMaskot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20new%20study%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwfh-work-from-home-decreases-productivity-18-percent-study-rto-2023-8%5C%22%3Eproductivity%20was%20lower%20in%20a%20group%20of%20workers%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20WFH%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20study%20also%20surveyed%20workers%20on%20their%20preferences%20for%20WFH%20versus%20coming%20into%20the%20office.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20the%20study's%20authors%20told%20Insider%20those%20who%20prefer%20WFH%20are%20also%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20distracted%26quot%3B%20at%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20study%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-recession-economic-outlook-labor-productivity-negative-impact-workplace-trends-2023-6%5C%22%3Eworker%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20attracting%20buzz%20for%20a%20finding%20that%20could%20fuel%20the%20case%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-ceos-remote-work-office-careers-2023-6%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20trying%20to%20bring%20workers%20back%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20found%20that%20randomly%20selected%20data-entry%20workers%20in%20Chennai%2C%20India%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwfh-work-from-home-decreases-productivity-18-percent-study-rto-2023-8%5C%22%3E18%25%20less-productive%20working%20from%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20from%20the%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20study%20also%20uncovered%20another%20surprising%20statistic%20about%20the%20kinds%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-earning-workers-prefer-wfh-remote-work-mckinsey-survey-2023-7%5C%22%3Eworkers%20who%20opt%20to%20work%20from%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20found%20that%20those%20who%20prefer%20to%20work%20from%20home%20are%20%E2%80%94%20at%20baseline%20%E2%80%94%20actually%2012%25%20faster%20and%20more%20accurate%20in%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20study%20found%20that%20these%20workers%20are%20approximately%2027%25%20less-productive%20at%20home%20than%20at%20the%20office.%20Those%20who%20prefer%20to%20work%20from%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20they're%20initially%20slower%20or%20less-accurate%20%E2%80%94%20are%20just%2013%25%20less-productive%20when%20working%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Atkin%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20economics%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20and%20one%20of%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20study%2C%20told%20Insider%20by%20email%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20find%20that%20those%20whose%20productivity%20suffers%20relatively%20more%20when%20they%20work%20from%20home%20are%20actually%20more%20likely%2C%20not%20less%2C%20to%20choose%20WFH.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20are%20workers%20opting%20to%20work%20in%20settings%20where%20they're%20less-productive%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20explanation%20for%20why%20workers%20are%20choosing%20to%20work%20where%20they%20are%20less%20productive%20is%20that%20the%20workers%20who%20most%20need%20to%20be%20around%20the%20house%20during%20the%20workday%20are%20exactly%20the%20workers%20who%20are%20most%20distracted%20working%20from%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Atkin%20wrote%20to%20Insider.%20These%20could%20include%20subsets%20of%20workers%20who%20need%20to%20care%20for%20children%2C%20tend%20to%20household%20responsibilities%20during%20the%20day%2C%20or%20are%20from%20poorer%20households%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nber.org%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fworking_papers%2Fw31515%2Fw31515.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20summarizing%20the%20study's%20finding%20noted.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20workers'%20preferences%20and%20circumstances%20are%20bound%20to%20vary%20across%20countries%2C%20and%20industries%2C%20the%20study's%20findings%20could%20offer%20a%20springboard%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-saw-productivity-increase-throughout-the-pandemic-but-employee-burnout-is-an-ongoing-concern-2021-10%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20to%20design%20policies%20that%20optimize%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20offering%20their%20employees%20flexibility.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAtkin%20suggests%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrid-working-model-wfh-work-from-home-policy-office-trends-2023-7%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20work%20arrangements%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20an%20answer%2C%20even%20though%20they%20weren't%20explored%20in%20this%20particular%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20speculate%20that%20being%20able%20to%20WFH%20several%20days%20a%20week%2C%20and%20go%20the%20office%20the%20other%20days%2C%20may%20balance%20workers'%20demands%20for%20WFH%20with%20the%20productivity%20costs%20we%20find%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20provide%20face-to-face%20training%20and%20team%20interactions%20that%20are%20major%20drivers%20of%20productivity%20in%20more%20complex%20job%20settings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-who-prefer-work-from-home-wfh-are-less-productive-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691658421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d295a87d2e9000194698a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-who-prefer-work-from-home-wfh-are-less-productive-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Workers%20who%20prefer%20to%20work%20from%20home%20are%20less-productive%20when%20they%20do%20so%2C%20a%20new%20study%20suggests.%20Other%20duties%20might%20intru