3Cp%3EThe%20RPF%20constable%E2%80%99s%20act%20shows%20that%20militant%20Hindutva%20groups%20no%20longer%20need%20to%20train%20or%20arm%20people%20to%20commit%20violence%20against%20Muslims.%20They%20are%20now%20in%20the%20state%20apparatus%20and%20they%20will%20do%20it%20voluntarily%20or%20habitually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Muslims%20resist%20hate%2C%20all%20hell%20breaks%20loose%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20situation%20of%20mob%20violence%20in%20which%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20are%20involved%2C%20the%20chances%20of%20Muslims%20getting%20arrested%20in%20greater%20numbers%20are%20high.%20As%20we%20saw%20in%20Nuh%20recently%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnuh-demolitions-residents-due-process-damages%5C%22%3Einstant%20punishment%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20meted%20out%20to%20one%20side%20without%20following%20any%20procedure%2C%20by%20bulldozing%20their%20houses%20and%20business%20establishments.%20It%20has%20now%20become%20a%20norm%20to%20inflict%20such%20retribution%20on%20Muslims%20after%20every%20communal%20incident.%20We%20ask%2C%20without%20getting%20any%20response%2C%20why%20the%20houses%20of%20Muslims%20who%20were%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20violence%20are%20being%20demolished%20%E2%80%93%20as%20if%20instantly%20demolishing%20the%20houses%20of%20those%20who%20might%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20any%20manner%20is%20somehow%20justified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20other%20questions%3A%20Has%20the%20bulldozer%20now%20been%20accepted%20as%20the%20first%20instrument%20of%20justice%20or%20punishment%20for%20any%20crime%2C%20even%20before%20the%20examination%20of%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20incident%3F%20Why%20is%20it%20that%20it%20is%20directed%20only%20against%20Muslims%3F%20For%20example%2C%20has%20the%20house%20of%20the%20police%20officer%20accused%20of%20four%20murders%20on%20the%20moving%20train%20been%20demolished%3F%20What%20about%20the%20house%20of%20the%20lik