20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharidwar-anti-muslim-hate-speech-laws-broken%5C%22%3Ehate%20assemblies%20calling%20for%20the%20annihilation%20of%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20not%20seen%20as%20disturbing%20the%20peace.%20Similarly%2C%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fseven-incidents-across-india-where-the-hindutva-brigade-disrupted-christmas-celebrations%5C%22%3Epeople%20barge%20in%20when%20Christmas%20is%20being%20celebrated%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20church%20and%20raise%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20slogans%2C%20it%20is%20not%20seen%20as%20a%20problem%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20breach%20of%20peace%20only%20when%20these%20elements%20are%20stopped%20from%20doing%20what%20they%20want.%20The%20police%20officer%20Prabhakar%20Chaudhary%20stopped%20the%20VHP%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20from%20playing%20loud%20music%20outside%20a%20mosque%20in%20Bareilly%20and%20creating%20a%20ruckus%20there.%20He%20ordered%20a%20lathi%20charge%20to%20disperse%20them.%20As%20a%20punishment%2C%20the%20officer%20was%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EImagine%20a%20similar%20situation%20in%20which%20a%20group%20of%20Muslims%20do%20what%20the%20VHP%20or%20Bajrang%20Dal%20do%20regularly.%20Would%20they%20be%20allowed%3F%20The%20fate%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fazam-khan-conviction-hate-speech-case-set-aside%5C%22%3EAzam%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20before%20us.%20His%20legislative%20assembly%20membership%20has%20been%20taken%20away%20after%20he%20was%20sentenced%20to%20three%20years%20in%20jail%20for%20a%20hate%20speech%20against%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%20Just%20recollect%20some%20of%20the%20speeches%20made%20by%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20prime%20minister.%20If%20the%20same%20standards%20were%20applied%20to%20them%2C%20they%20would%20also%20be%20in%20jail.%20But%2C%20we%20know%20that%20will%20never%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20targeting%20of%20Muslims%20on%20TV%20channels%20every%20day%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20legitimate%20exercise%20of%20free%20speech.%20No%20breach%20of%20the%20peace%20here!%20Muslims%20should%20just%20switch%20off%20the%20TV%20if%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20abuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeave%20aside%20the%20organised%20hate%20campaigns%2C%20now%20unaffiliated%20individuals%20promote%20this%20hate%20campaign%20voluntarily%20in%20their%20family%20or%20school%20or%20neighbourhood%20groups%20and%20friend%20circles.%20Everything%20remains%20peaceful%20till%20the%20hate%20is%20challenged%20by%20some%20%E2%80%98crazy%E2%80%99%20member%20of%20the%20group.%20Then%20she%20or%20he%20is%20blamed%20for%20disturbing%20the%20tranquility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20shift%20the%20focus%20from%20Muslims%20and%20instead%20talk%20about%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Hintuvawadi%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20their%20actions%20and%20their%20speeches%20%E2%80%93%20and%20about%20Hindu%20society%20in%20general.%20If%20you%20are%20Hindu%20and%20your%20peace%20of%20mind%20is%20not%20disturbed%20even%20after%20this%2C%20then%20the%20Hindu%20community%20is%20surely%20doomed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691657124000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01202349%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-01T202233.079.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-violence-rpf-constables-murder-new-phase-anti-muslim-hate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20targeted%20killing%20of%20three%20Muslims%20on%20a%20moving%20train%20by%20a%20cop%20was%20the%20act%20of%20an%20individual%2C%20the%20violence%20in%20Nuh%20is%20organised.%20It%20is%20this%20combination%20of%20hate%20that%20Hindutvawadis%20have%20been%20empl