2FIMG_1737.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20quite%20refreshing%20to%20note%20that%20just%20three%20days%20before%20the%20%E2%80%98August%20Kranti%20Divas%E2%80%99%20on%20August%209%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20very%20respectfully%20recalled%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20launched%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20at%20a%20function%20to%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20the%20redevelopment%20of%20numerous%20railway%20stations%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFriends%E2%80%A69th%20August%20holds%20historical%20significance%20as%20the%20momentous%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20was%20launched%20on%20this%20date.%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20gave%20the%20clarion%20call%20of%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20igniting%20a%20new%20surge%20of%20energy%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20India%20towards%20independence.%20Inspired%20by%20this%20spirit%2C%20today%20the%20entire%20nation%20is%20raising%20its%20voice%20against%20all%20evils%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20surprise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraise%20for%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%2C%20coming%20from%20a%20leader%20thoroughly%20moulded%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20ideology%2C%20is%20quite%20heartening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20well-known%20fact%20that%20during%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%2C%20the%20RSS%20sided%20with%20V.D.%20Savarkar%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20Mahasabha.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98do%20or%20die%E2%80%99%20call%20by%20the%20Mahatma%2C%20it%20%E2%80%9Ckept%20itself%20within%20the%20law%2C%20and%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20refrained%20from%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20disturbances%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20August%201942%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bombay%20Home%20Department%20observed%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20head%2C%20M.S.%20Golwalkar%20and%20whole%20timers%20Deendayal%20Upadhyaya%2C%20Balraj%20Madhok%2C%20and%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20during%20this%20period%2C%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20Movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20and%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESavarkar%20was%20openly%20against%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement.%20He%20issued%20a%20statement%20urging%20Hindu%20Mahasabhaites%20and%20%E2%80%9CHindus%20in%20general%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20to%20extend%20any%20active%20support%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20Movement.%20%20He%20had%20continued%20by%20saying%20that%20any%20movement%20the%20Congress%20inspired%20would%20%E2%80%9Cprove%20most%20detrimental%E2%80%9D%20to%20Hindu%20interests%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20integrity%20and%20strength%20of%20India%20as%20a%20nation%20and%20a%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyamaprasad%20Mukherjee%20of%20the%20Bengal%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%2C%20as%20cabinet%20minister%20of%20the%20A.K.%20Fazlul%20Haq%20government%20of%20Bengal%2C%20was%20not%20to%20be%20left%20behind.%20Haq%20had%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20just%20a%20little%20over%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20presented%20the%20Lahore%20Resolution%20of%201940%20for%20creation%20of%20Pakistan%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Muslim%20League.%20Mukherjee%20wrote%20to%20the%20Governor%20on%20July%2026%2C%201942%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20is%20how%20to%20combat%20this%20movement%20(Quit%20India)%20in%20Bengal%3F%E2%80%A6It%20should%20be%20possible%20for%20us%2C%20especially%20responsible%20Ministers%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20the%20public%20that%20the%20freedom%20for%20which%20the%20Congress%20has%20started%20the%20movement%2C%20already%20belongs%20to%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%A6Indians%20have%20to%20trust%20the%20British%2C%20not%20for%20the%20sake%20for%20Britain%2C%20not%20for%20any%20advantage%20that%20the%20British%20might%20gain%2C%20but%20for%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20defence%20and%20freedom%20of%20the%20province%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESavarkar%E2%80%99s%20diktat%20on%20the%20Mahasabhaites%20was%20already%20in%20force.%20He%20had%20announced%2C%20in%20this%20War%20against%20Japan%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9CHindudom%20must%20ally%20unhesitatingly%2C%20in%20a%20spirit%20of%20responsive%20co-operation%20with%20the%20war%20effort%20of%20the%20(British)%20Indian%20government%E2%80%A6by%20joining%20the%20Army%2C%20Navy%20and%20the%20Aerial%20forces%20in%20as%20large%20a%20number%E2%80%A6especially%20in%20the%20provinces%20of%20Bengal%20and%20Assam%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20was%20working%20on%20the%20military%20strategies%20to%20take%20help%20of%20the%20German%20and%20Japanese%20forces%20to%20liberate%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fquit-india-the-last-nail-in-the-coffin-of-the-british-empire%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Quit%20India%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20Last%20Nail%20in%20the%20Coffin%20of%20the%20British%20Empire%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Boses%20on%20Savarkar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERash%20Behari%20Bose%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army%2C%20who%20had%20in%201938%20opened%20up%20a%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20branch%20in%20Japan%2C%20got%20perturbed%20at%20Savarkar%E2%80%99s%20volte%20face.%20He%20made%20frantic%20appeal%20to%20him%20on%20March%2021%2C%201942%20from%20Tokyo%2C%20%E2%80%9CEngland%E2%80%99s%20difficulty%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20opportunity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlease%20do%20not%20let%20your%20vision%20be%20blurred%20at%20this%20critical%20moment%E2%80%A6Japan%20and%20her%20allies%2C%20being%20England%E2%80%99s%20enemy%2C%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20friend%E2%80%A6I%20have%20decided%20to%20mobilise%20all%20my%20Indian%20brothers%20in%20a%20supreme%20effort%20to%20strike%20at%20the%20fetters%E2%80%A6But%20I%20shall%20not%20succeed%20unless%20yourself%20and%20other%20leaders%20at%20home%20support%20me%E2%80%A6Then%20would%20you%20fail%20now%20when%20the%20long%20awaited%20chance%20for%20its%20success%20has%20fallen%20into%20our%20very%20laps%3F%E2%80%A6India%20has%20nothing%20in%20common%20with%20England.%20But%20with%20Japan%20she%20is%20culturally%20united.%20Then%2C%20why%20side%20with%20England%20in%20a%20war%20against%20Japan%3F%20Rather%20why%20not%20side%20with%20Japan%20and%20destroy%20the%20British%20power%3F%E2%80%A6I%20have%20nothing%20more%20to%20request.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Savarkar%20paid%20no%20heed%20to%20Rashbehari%E2%80%99s%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20disgust%2C%20Netaji%20had%20written%20in%20his%20%3Cem%3EIndian%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EStruggle%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMr%20Savarkar%20seemed%20to%20be%20oblivious%20of%20the%20international%20situation%20and%20was%20only%20thinking%20how%20Hindus%20could%20secure%20military%20training%20by%20entering%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20army%20in%20India%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20at%20this%20juncture%20that%20not%20only%20did%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20and%20RSS%20oppose%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%2C%20rulers%20of%20the%20Princely%20states%20too%20opposed%20it.%20The%20Muslim%20League%20(ML)%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20stayed%20aloof.%20Despite%20CPI%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20keeping%20aloof%2C%20large%20number%20of%20communist%20activists%20participated%20in%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetaji%20on%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetaji%2C%20who%20had%20left%20India%20differing%20with%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20soft%20approach%20towards%20the%20British%2C%20on%20reading%20the%20news%20in%20Berlin%20of%20Gandhi%20launching%20the%20%E2%80%98Quit%20India%E2%80%99%20movement%20told%20his%20close%20associate%20A.C.N.%20Nambiar%20that%20he%20need%20to%20be%20with%20Gandhi%20at%20that%20stage.%20In%20his%20message%20over%20the%20%E2%80%98Azad%20Hind%20Radio%E2%80%99%20he%20called%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20%E2%80%9Cnon-violent%20guerrilla%20warfare%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20the%20leaders%20in%20India%20and%20the%20countrymen%2C%20over%20radio%20on%20August%2017%2C%201942%2C%20%E2%80%9CComrades%E2%80%A6the%20movement%20in%20India%20has%20been%20continuing%20with%20unabated%20vigour%2C%20and%20has%20been%20spreading%20like%20wild%20fire%20from%20towns%20to%20the%20countryside%E2%80%A6I%20would%20request%20Mr%20Jinnah%2C%20Mr%20Savarkar%2C%20and%20all%20those%20leaders%20who%20still%20think%20of%20a%20compromise%20with%20the%20British%2C%20to%20realise%20once%20for%20all%20that%20in%20the%20world%20of%20tomorrow%20there%20will%20be%20no%20British%20Empire%E2%80%A6Inquilab%20Zindabad.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20every%20section%20of%20the%20community%20to%20participate%20in%20this%20movement.%20He%20suggested%20that%20tactics%20of%20guerrilla%20war%20need%20to%20be%20applied%20and%20gave%20guidance%20on%20the%20same.%20He%20called%20for%20boycott%2C%20interruptions%2C%20disruptions%2C%20destruction%20and%20demonstrations%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be%2C%20of%20all%20British%20establishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2FQuit-India-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20procession%20in%20Bangalore%20during%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-163455%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22429%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20procession%20in%20Bangalore%20during%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20lakh%20arrests%20were%20made%20which%20included%20all%20top%20leadership%20of%20Congress%2C%20including%20Gandhi.%20Mass%20fines%20were%20levied%20and%20demonstrators%20were%20subjected%20to%20public%20flogging.%20According%20to%20the%20British%20estimate%2C%2063%20officers%20were%20killed%2C%202%2C000%20officers%20wounded%2C%20and%20200%20officers%20fled.%20Over%201%2C000%20freedom%20fighters%20were%20killed%20(Congress%20estimated%204%2C000-10%2C000)%20and%20over%203%2C000%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%E2%80%98Congress%20Radio%E2%80%99%20was%20set%20up%20clandestinely%20in%20Bombay%20as%20the%20broadcasting%20mouthpiece%20of%20the%20Congress.%20It%20could%20be%20heard%20all%20over%20India%20and%20up%20to%20Burma.%20The%20station%20continued%20to%20broadcast%20recorded%20messages%20from%20prominent%20leaders%20of%20the%20movement%20including%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%20It%20reported%20on%20incidents%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20countering%20the%20narratives%20from%20the%20official%20state%20broadcaster%20%E2%80%98All%20India%20Radio%E2%80%99.%20Due%20to%20its%20guerrilla%20tactics%20applied%20the%20government%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20jam%20the%20broadcast.%20It%20took%20them%20three%20months%20to%20finally%20arrest%20all%20those%20associated%20with%20this%20successful%20liaison%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%E2%80%99%20jibe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20was%20quick%20to%20pick%20up%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20reference%20to%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20as%20%E2%80%9Cigniting%20a%20new%20surge%20of%20energy%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20India%20towards%20independence%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20mantra%20given%20by%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20mentioned%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20utterance%20as%20%E2%80%9Cour%20victory%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20considering%20those%20who%20did%20not%20remember%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20for%2075%20years%20are%20doing%20so%20now.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYour%20political%20forefathers%20pitted%20Indians%20against%20Indians%2C%20supported%20British%20rule%2C%20served%20as%20informers%20for%20them%20and%20strongly%20opposed%20Quit%20India.%20They%20had%20a%20suspect%20role%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20assassinate%20Gandhi.%20They%20opposed%20the%20Tricolour.%20They%20did%20not%20hoist%20it%20till%2052%20years%20of%20Independence.%20Sardar%20Patel%20had%20to%20warn%20them%20over%20boycotting%20the%20tricolour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Cstrong%3Ereformist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20departure%20from%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20and%20RSS%20view%20of%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20is%20not%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay%2C%20in%20his%202017%20article%2C%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fquit-india-modi-sangh-parivar%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Position%20On%20Quit%20India%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Quite%20Match%20His%20Predecessors%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%2C%20had%20raised%20this%20question%20first%3A%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Modi%20the%20first%20saffron%20revisionist%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESumeru%20Roy%20Chaudhury%20is%20an%20architecture%20graduate%20from%20IIT%2C%20Kharagpur.%20He%20was%20the%20chief%20architect%20of%20the%20CPWD.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691653869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30091446%2FIMG_1737.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fquit-india-movement-narendra-modi-gandhi-netaji%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Praise%20for%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%2C%20coming%20from%20a%20leader%20as%20thoroughly%20moulded%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh's%20ideology%20as%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20is%20quite%20heartening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fquit-india-movement-narendra-modi-gandhi-netaji%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22King%20Of%20Kotha%20Trailer%3A%20SRK%2C%20Suriya%20Cheer%20For%20Dulquer%20Salmaan%22%2C%22content%