e%20of%20our%20state%20in%20the%20First%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20has%20been%20written%20as%20Kerala.%20This%20Assembly%20is%20unanimously%20requesting%20the%20Union%20Government%20to%20take%20immediate%20steps%20under%20Article%203%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20the%20state%20to%20Keralam%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkerala%2Fkerala-assembly-unanimously-passes-resolution-to-change-official-name-of-state-to-keralam%2Farticle67175490.ece%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%203%20in%20the%20constitution%20deals%20with%20the%20formation%20of%20new%20states%20and%20the%20alteration%20of%20areas%2C%20boundaries%2C%20or%20names%20of%20existing%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-politics%2Fkerala-to-rename-keralam-origin-8884600%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%20several%20theories%20about%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Kerala%E2%80%99.%20It%20says%20the%20earliest%20epigraphic%20record%20that%20mentions%20Kerala%20is%20emperor%20Asoka%E2%80%99s%20Rock%20Edict%20II%20of%20257%20BC.%C2%A0%20The%20inscription%20refers%20to%20the%20local%20ruler%20as%20Keralaputra%20(Sanskrit%20for%20%E2%80%9Cson%20of%20Kerala%E2%80%9D)%2C%20and%20also%20%E2%80%9Cson%20of%20Chera%E2%80%9D%20referring%20to%20the%20Chera%20dynasty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20movement%20for%20the%20unification%20of%20Malayalam-speaking%20regions%20had%20been%20gathering%20momentum%20since%20the%201920s%2C%20which%20called%20for%20the%20merger%20of%20Malabar%2C%20Kochi%2C%20and%20Travancore%20into%20one%20territory.%20On%20July%201%2C%201949%2C%20two%20princely%20states%20of%20Travancore%20and%20Kochi%20were%20integrated%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20Travancore-Cochin%20state.%20Later%2C%20on%20November%201%2C%201956%2C%20the%20present-day%20Kerala%20came%20into%20being%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20formation%20of%20linguistic%20states.%20The%20Syed%20Fazl%20Ali%20Commission%20recommended%20that%20states%20be%20reorganised%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20common%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20not%20necessary%20for%20renaming%20cities%2C%20however%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20renaming%20states%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20nod%20is%20mandatory.%20A%20constitutional%20amendment%20is%20necessary%20for%20such%20a%20change%20to%20take%20effect%2C%20requiring%20parliamentary%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20proposal%20is%20received%20from%20the%20state%20government%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20begins%20its%20process.%20It%20seeks%20No%20Objection%20Certificates%20(NOCs)%20from%20several%20agencies%20such%20as%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Railways%2C%20Intelligence%20Bureau%2C%20Department%20of%20Posts%2C%20Survey%20of%20India%2C%20and%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20to%20allow%20such%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20proposal%20is%20accepted%2C%20the%20resolution%2C%20introduced%20as%20a%20Bill%20in%20the%20parliament%2C%20becomes%20a%20law%20and%20the%20name%20of%20the%20state%20is%20changed%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691652659000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F28124329%2Fdc-Cover-j5v1mqcmbp6o50fqg1vstj84n2-20160628134359.Medi_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkerala-assembly-passes-unanimous-resolution-to-rename-state-as-keralam-writes-to-centre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20'Keralam'%20is%20the%20accepted%20and%20common%20usage%20in%20Malayalam%2C%20the%20state%20is%20generally%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98Kerala'%20in%20official%20records%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20English.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkerala-assembly-passes-unanimous-resolution-to-rename-state-as-keralam-writes-to-centre%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Woman%20Was%20Attacked%20By%20Snake%20That%20Fell%20From%20The%20Sky%2C%20Then%20A%20Hawk%20Dived%20In%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2025%2C%20a%2064-year-old%20woman%20named%20Peggy%20Jones%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20were%20finishing%20a%20day%20of%20yard%20work%20at%20their%20property%20in%20Silsbee%2C%20Texas.%20Then%20suddenly%2C%20a%20snake%20fell%20from%20the%20sky%2C%20wrapping%20itself%20around%20Mrs%20Jones's%20right%20forearm.%20The%20woman%20tried%20to%20shake%20the%20snake%20loose%20but%20it%20refused%20to%20let%20her%20go%20and%20began%20striking%20her%20in%20the%20face.%20Moments%20later%2C%20a%20hawk%20swooped%20down%20and%20began%20attacking%20her%20arm%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20reclaim%20its%20lost%20prey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Jones%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F09%2Fus%2Ftexas-woman-snake-hawk-sky.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20immediately%20screamed%20and%20started%20swinging%20my%20arm%20to%20shake%20the%20snake%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20screaming%2C%20'Jesus%2C%20help%20me%2C%20please%2C%20Jesus%2C%20help%20me!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20snake%20was%20squeezing%20so%20hard%2C%20and%20I%20was%20waving%20my%20arms%20in%20the%20air.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20snake%20was%20striking%20in%20my%20face%2C%20it%20struck%20my%20glasses%20a%20couple%20of%20times...%20I%20was%20slinging%20and%20slinging%2C%20he%20was%20striking%20and%20striking%2C%20and%20he%20just%20kept%20hanging%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fsnake-hawk-attack-texas-peggy-jones-silsbee%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20brown-and-white%20hawk%20accidentally%20dropped%20the%20four-and-a-half-long%20creature%20on%20her.%20The%20bird%20swooped%20down%20to%20reclaim%20its%20meal%20from%20Mrs%20Jones'%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hawk%20snatched%2C%20scratched%20and%20jabbed%20at%20her%20arm%2C%20reported%20New%20York%20Times.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20the%20bird%20dragged%20Mrs%20Jones's%20arm%20up%20into%20the%20air.%20It%20stabbed%20her%20with%20its%20talons%20repeatedly%20as%20it%20attempted%20to%20snatch%20back%20its%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20snake%20was%20removed%20from%20her%20arm%20and%20she%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20by%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20puncture%20wounds%2C%20cuts%2C%20abrasions%2C%20scratches%20and%20severe%20bruising%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20CBS%20News%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20snake's%20attacks%20on%20her%20face%20damaged%20her%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20described%20the%20attack%20as%20severely%20traumatic%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20thought%20she%20was%20going%20to%20die%20and%20has%20had%20trouble%20sleeping%20since%20it%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20the%20media%20outlet%20that%20she%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20wildlife%20encounters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20actually%20seen%20a%20hawk%20pick%20up%20a%20snake.%20That's%20something%20they%20do%2C%20that's%20how%20they%20kill%20their%20prey%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20concluded%20by%20saying%20that%20this%20incident%20will%20stay%20in%20her%20mind%20for%20a%20long%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691652300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ffilavt2o_peggy-jones_625x300_10_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-was-attacked-by-snake-that-fell-from-the-sky-then-a-hawk-dived-in-4285691%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Texas%20woman%20