alry-over-the-years%2Farticleshow%2F102593151.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20'Practical'%20to%20Start%20with%2013A%20Amendment%20Without%20Police%20Powers%3A%20Sri%20Lanka%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26231515%2FAll-party-leaders-meeting-03.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20August%209%2C%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpractical%E2%80%9D%20to%20initially%20focus%20on%20implementing%20the%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20constitutional%20amendment%20on%20devolution%20without%20police%20control%20to%20the%20provincial%20councils.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmd.gov.lk%2Fnews%2Flets-collectively-advance-the-13th-amendment-to-the-constitution-for-the-future-betterment-of-the-nation%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20special%20statement%20to%20parliament%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Wickremesinghe%20acknowledged%20that%20police%20powers%20in%20the%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20amendment%20have%20%E2%80%9Cemerged%20as%20the%20most%20delicate%20issue%20in%20the%20transfer%20of%20authority%20to%20the%20Provincial%20Councils%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%2C%20I%20propose%20that%20it%20might%20be%20more%20practical%20for%20us%20to%20initially%20focus%20on%20reaching%20consensus%20concerning%20other%20powers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20advisable%20to%20progress%20step%20by%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWickremesinghe%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cprioritising%20sensitive%20matters%20could%20potentially%20hinder%20the%20attainment%20of%20any%20mutual%20agreement%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20constitutional%20amendment%20was%20a%20result%20of%20the%201987%20India-Sri%20Lanka%20accord%20which%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20provinces%20and%20devolution%20of%20land%20and%20police%20powers%20to%20the%20elected%20provincial%20councils.%20While%20the%20provinces%20have%20been%20created%2C%20the%20powers%20of%20land%20and%20police%20have%20still%20not%20been%20devolved%20due%20to%20opposition%20from%20all%20the%20Sinhala%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20the%20full%20implementation%20of%20the%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20amendment%2C%20which%20was%20also%20reiterated%20during%20Wickremesinghe%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20New%20Delhi%20last%20month.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20visit%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamil%20lawmakers%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20ask%20him%20to%20pressurise%20Wickremesinghe%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20amendment%20and%20holding%20the%20much-delayed%20provincial%20council%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20returning%20to%20Colombo%2C%20Wikremesinghe%20had%20convened%20an%20all-party%20conference%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20reconciliation%2C%20which%20he%20admitted%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20failure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20during%20the%20conference%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20arrive%20at%20a%20comprehensive%20agreement%20on%20power%20devolution.%20Divergent%20perspectives%20on%20a%20specific%20national%20decentralisation%20program%20were%20evident.%20It%20became%20apparent%20that%20certain%20political%20parties%20were%20hesitant%20to%20share%20their%20ideas%2C%20possibly%20due%20to%20past%20negative%20experiences%20from%20prior%20all-party%20conferences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPresenting%20a%20series%20of%20proposals%20regarding%20the%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20amendment%2C%20Wickremesinghe%20called%20for%20political%20parties%20to%20express%20their%20views.%20%E2%80%9CTaking%20all%20these%20viewpoints%20into%20careful%20consideration%2C%20the%20responsibility%20of%20arriving%20at%20the%20final%20decision%20regarding%20the%20role%20and%20future%20of%20provincial%20councils%20rests%20solely%20with%20this%20honourable%20council%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20indicated%20that%20the%20provincial%20elections%20can%20only%20be%20held%20after%20there%20are%20legal%20changes%20made%20to%20legal%20framework%20governing%20the%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20criticism%20that%20the%20government%20was%20%E2%80%9Cselling%20out%E2%80%9D%2C%20Wickremesinghe%20stated%20that%20no%20one%20could%20progress%20alone%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20too%20especially%20in%20the%20instance%20of%20a%20nation%20emerging%20from%20an%20unprecedented%20economic%20crisis%2C%20as%20has%20been%20the%20experience%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20must%20be%20understood%20that%20engaging%20in%20a%20robust%20relationship%20with%20our%20closest%20neighbour%20India%20would%20undoubtedly%20strengthen%20our%20ability%20towards%20ensuring%20mutually%20beneficial%20cooperation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691638554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26231515%2FAll-party-leaders-meeting-03.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmore-practical-to-start-with-13a-amendment-without-police-powers-sri-lanka-president%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20special%20statement%20to%20parliament%2C%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20said%20that%20police%20powers%20in%20the%2013