ong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20also%20saw%20two%20Union%20ministers%20warring%20with%20National%20Conference%20MP%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20over%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20work%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20said%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20should%20act%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20whole%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20PM%20does%20not%20represent%20only%20one%20colour.%20He%20represents%20the%201.4%20billion%20people%20of%20India.%20I%20tried%20to%20bring%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20back%20home%20when%20Gujral%20was%20PM%20and%20forces%20across%20the%20border%20killed%20innocent%20Kashmiri%20Pandits.%20We%20stopped%20the%2050%20vehicles%20to%20bring%20them%20back%20home.%20How%20many%20Pandits%20have%20you%20brought%20back%20in%20ten%20years%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%20Nityanand%20Rai%20stood%20up%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cwrong%E2%80%9D%20to%20say%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20done%20anything%20for%20Kashmiri%20Pandits.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20misleading%E2%80%9D%2C%20Rai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20also%20said%20that%20whether%20it%20is%20Kashmir%20or%20Manipur%2C%20the%20message%20of%20love%20should%20be%20sent%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20work%20with%20love%20and%20win%20people%E2%80%99s%20hearts.%20Love%20is%20the%20only%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20MP%20Harsimrat%20Kaur%20Badal%20also%20said%20that%20the%20politics%20of%20hate%20will%20not%20solve%20anything%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20doing%20politics%20of%20hate%2C%20the%20government%20should%20provide%20its%20healing%20touch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20from%20the%20YSRCP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20however%2C%20received%20support%20from%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20(YSCRP)%2C%20which%20said%20that%20while%20the%20party%20will%20support%20the%20government%20in%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20Manipur%20needs%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP.V.%20Mithun%20Reddy%2C%20YSRCP%20MP%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cheinous%20crimes%20against%20women%E2%80%9D%20are%20being%20seen%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEthnic%20violence%20needs%20to%20be%20curbed.%20Both%20the%20ethnic%20groups%20need%20to%20be%20made%20to%20sit%20for%20a%20dialogue.%20This%20is%20really%20shameful%20that%20this%20is%20happening%20in%20our%20country%20where%20we%20preach%20unity%20in%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAddress%20the%20source%20of%20the%20problem%20through%20meaningful%20dialogue.%20A%20strong%20Manipur%20means%20a%20strong%20India.%20YSRCP%20believes%20that%20this%20no-confidence%20motion%20does%20not%20carry%20much%20value%2C%20because%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20has%20an%20absolute%20majority.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20tussle%20between%20two%20alliances%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20urge%20the%20government%20to%20sort%20out%20Manipur%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20government%20should%20act%20with%20all%20its%20might%20to%20ensure%20peace%20is%20restored.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20also%20saw%20speeches%20from%20Union%20minister%20Anupriya%20Patel%2C%20BJP%20MPs%20Heena%20Gavit%20and%20Ram%20Kirpal%20Yadav%2C%20along%20with%20opposition%20MPs%20like%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20MP%20K.%20Subbarayan%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691601343000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09222428%2FAmit-Anil-Chandra-Shah-in-Lok-Sabha.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famit-shah-defends-biren-singh-in-parliament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20over%20two-hour-long%20speech%2C%20Shah%20listed%20his%20governme