t.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fwanted-hong-kong-activist-says-parents-harassed-intimidated%2Famp_articleshow%2F102561548.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fwanted-hong-kong-activist-says-parents-harassed-intimidated%2Famp_articleshow%2F102561548.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Entrepreneur%E2%80%99s%20Agri-Tech%20Solution%20Helps%20Farmers%20Cut%20Water%20Use%20by%2040%25%20%26%20Increase%20Yield%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20water%20from%20five%20rivers%20including%20Cauvery%20and%20Hemavathi%2C%20farmers%20in%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20Mandya%20still%20faced%20water%20shortages%20in%20their%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalesh%20T%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20watching%20his%20grandfather%20cultivate%20sugarcane%2C%20observed%20that%20a%20nearby%20district%20Kolar%20with%20low%20water%20resources%20still%20flourished%20with%20crops%20and%20had%20happy%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20paddy%20plants%20need%202%20crore%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20hectare%20per%20season.%20But%20some%20farmers%20use%20close%20to%2020%2C000-30%2C000%20litres.%20They%20do%20not%20have%20a%20mechanism%20to%20measure%20that.%20So%2C%20the%20problem%20never%20was%20the%20lack%20of%20water%20resources%20but%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F225243%2Fkerala-man-innovation-water-plants-innovation-terrace-gardening-business-india-ser106%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eirrigation%20techniques.%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20when%20a%20farmer%20uses%20more%20water%20than%20required%2C%20the%20farms%20remain%20flooded%20with%20water%20for%20a%20maximum%20part%20of%20the%20season%20resulting%20in%20fungal%20diseases%20and%20hence%2C%20more%20spending%20on%20disease%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%202016%2C%20he%20launched%20CultYvate%2C%20a