0instant%20milk%20chillers%20because%20the%20locations%20are%20spread%20out.%20By%20the%20time%2C%20these%20communities%20transported%20milk%20from%20one%20hamlet%20to%20another%20and%20then%20to%20the%20dairy%2C%20the%20milk%20would%20go%20bad%20amid%20extreme%20temperatures%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20milk%20is%20brought%20to%20the%20dairy%20and%20milk%20processing%20units%20in%20Bajju%20village%20via%20delivery%20vans.%20Thereafter%2C%20products%20are%20made%20using%20camel%20and%20cow%20milk%2C%20which%20are%20then%20sold%20to%20300%20households%20across%20Bikaner%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20using%20a%20subscription%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20sells%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173064%2Fmilk-cow-camel-almond-coconut-yak-goat-soy-coconut-alternative-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecamel%20milk%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20camel%20milk%20biscuits%2C%20camel%20milk%20feta%20cheese%2C%20camel%20milk%20Cheshire%20cheese%2C%20A2%20cow%20%3Cem%3Ebilona%20ghee%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cold%20pressed%20oils%2C%20gluten-free%20black%20wheat%20flour%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakriti%20further%20informs%20that%20their%20cheese%20is%20now%20also%20procured%20by%20chefs%20in%20cities%20like%20Goa%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20to%20run%20such%20a%20startup%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20common%20for%20Indians%20to%20consume%20camel%20milk%20products.%20In%20the%20first%20year%2C%20most%20of%20our%20time%20was%20spent%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20camel%20milk%20products%2C%20which%20are%20highly%20nutritious%20superfoods.%20These%20products%20help%20people%20with%20diabetes%2C%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20cardiovascular%20disease.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-2-1691499158.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Genaram%20Raika%2C%20a%20camel%20herder%2C%20earns%20Rs%201%2C600%20a%20day%20by%20selling%20camel%20milk.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-2-1691499158.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-2-1691499158-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-2-1691499158-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-2-1691499158-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-2-1691499158-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326693%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGenaram%20Raika%2C%20a%20camel%20herder%2C%20earns%20Rs%201%2C600%20a%20day%20by%20selling%20camel%20milk.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20May%20last%20year%2C%20the%20communities%20have%20been%20able%20to%20collectively%20generate%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20small-scale%20household%20is%20able%20to%20earn%20an%20income%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2012%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20which%20was%20earlier%20zero!%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20numerous%20herders%20are%20including%20camels%20in%20their%20groups%20because%20they%20can%20once%20again%20make%20money%20from%20them.%20At%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20Pushkar%20%3Cem%3Emela%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20price%20of%20camels%20in%20the%20local%20market%20also%20increased%20to%20Rs%2035%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aakriti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Genaram%20Raika%2