F298187%2Fbihar-snake-man-fights-superstition-to-rescue-snakes-sets-up-animal-centre%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20field%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20started%20operating%20mobile%20medical%20units%20in%202017.%20The%20ambulances%20are%20equipped%20with%20emergency%20oxygen%20and%20medical%20facilities%20to%20provide%20on-the-spot%20treatment.%20Aditi%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20para%20veterinary%20worker%2C%20driver%20and%20handler%20in%20each%20unit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20treating%20the%20animal%20on%20the%20field%2C%20we%20involve%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20particular%20area.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20when%20the%20community%20gets%20involved%20that%20the%20animal%20stands%20a%20chance%20of%20living%20a%20better%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aditi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20work%20is%20not%20over%20after%20treating%20the%20animal%20on%20day%20one.%20We%20follow%20up%20daily%20till%20the%20animal%20is%20better.%20We%20teach%20residents%20who%20are%20around%20the%20animals%20how%20to%20take%20care%20of%20them%2C%20how%20often%20they%20have%20to%20be%20given%20saline%2C%20how%20to%20apply%20the%20ointments%20for%20them%2C%20etc%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20says%20that%20they%20educate%20people%20wherever%20they%20go%20on%20what%20diet%20can%20be%20offered%20to%20cats%20and%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20people%20give%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%20to%20dogs%20and%20cats%2C%20which%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t.%20They%20are%20usually%20lactose%20intolerant.%20%5BWe%20tell%20them%20that%5D%20even%20rotis%20or%20any%20wheat%20and%20maida%20products%20should%20be%20avoided.%20It%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20give%20khichdi.%20So%20we%20try%20our%20best%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20animal%20is%20cared%20for%20well.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20case%20of%20paralysis%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20defecate%20themselves.%20We%20teach%20people%20how%20to%20help%20them%20do%20that.%20For%20tick