a%20hoarder%2C%20expressing%20her%20fondness%20for%20collecting%20items%2C%20particularly%20bottles.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20never%20have%20enough%20of%20them.%20I%20would%20go%20to%20scrap%20dealers%20and%20wander%20around%20looking%20for%20pretty-looking%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20exclaims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20soon%20enough%20she%20found%20herself%20in%20a%20quirky%20predicament%20%E2%80%94%20her%20house%20had%20become%20a%20battleground%20of%20bottles!%20With%20a%20twinkle%20in%20her%20eye%2C%20she%20confesses%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20breathing%20space%20left.%20My%20poor%20kids%20teased%20me%20relentlessly%2C%20but%20hey%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20part%20with%20my%20precious%20collection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20ago%2C%20someone%20wise%20aptly%20expressed%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20person%E2%80%99s%20trash%20is%20another%20person%E2%80%99s%20treasure.%E2%80%9D%20Carrying%20the%20sentiment%20forward%2C%20Gayatri%20started%20to%20look%20for%20ways%20of%20using%20the%20mammoth%20amount%20of%20bottles%20in%20her%20storage%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20she%20found%20%E2%80%98Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%E2%80%99%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286048%2Fbest-home-decor-influencers-interior-design-diy-recycle-ideas-tips-on-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20venture%20that%20converts%20glass%20waste%20into%20pieces%20of%20home%20decor%20and%20utensils.%20Founded%20by%20Noida-based%20Madhuri%20Balodi%20and%20Amit%20Singh%2C%20the%20project%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314356%2Fkerala-woman-upcycles-waste-glass-into-home-decor-vapasee-sustainable-venture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollects%20glass%20bottles%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20ragpickers%20and%20customers%2C%20and%20converts%20them%20into%20serving%20sets%2C%20platters%2C%20drinking%20glasses%2C%20lamps%20and%20other%20such%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20never%20seen%20anyone%20do%20this%20before%2C%20so%20I%20spoke%20to%20them%2C%20I%20resonated%20with%20their%20ideology%20so%20much%20that%20I%20shipped%20six%20cartons%20full%20of%20bottles%20to%20them.%20They%20made%20me%20all%20sorts%20of%20things%20like%20planters%2C%20platters%2C%20vases%2C%20wine%20glasses%2C%20jars%20and%20lamps%20from%20these%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20quality%20of%20the%20products%20is%20so%20good%2C%20I%20have%20gifted%20so%20many%20of%20those%20pieces%20to%20my%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gayatri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETesting%20the%20waters%20of%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EGreen%20Sutra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20India%20produces%20three%20million%20tonnes%20of%20glass%20waste%20every%20year.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20only%2045%20percent%20is%20recycled%20while%20the%20rest%20ends%20up%20in%20landfills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Co-founders%20of%20Kavi%20The%20Poetry%20Art%20Project%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMadhuri%20Balodi%20and%20Amit%20Singh%2C%20co-founders%20of%20Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Madhuri%20Balodi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%2032-year-old%20Madhuri%2C%20sustainable%20living%20has%20always%20been%20a%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20realise%20how%20much%20harm%20we%20do%20to%20the%20environment%20with%20our%20daily%20activities.%20We%20might%20think%20that%20these%20glass%20bottles%20go%20to%20recycling%20but%20the%20ground%20reality%20is%20quite%20different.%20Most%20of%20them%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhuri%20met%20Amit%20while%20working%20in%20the%20media%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CAmit%20and%20I%20had%20a%20very%20similar%20outlook%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fa%3E%20We%20would%20chat%20about%20how%20we%20could%20do%20something%20about%20it%20and%20ended%20up%20brainstorming%20ideas%20for%20hours.%20Being%20in%20the%20media%20industry%2C%20both%20of%20us%20were%20exposed%20first-hand%20to%20innovators%20around%20the%20world%20who%20were%20working%20in%20the%20sustainability%20field.%20We%20often%20heard%20topics%20like%20solar%20energy%2C%20upcycling%2C%20reusing%2C%20and%20recycling%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20at%20so%20many%20people%20working%20towards%20sustainability%2C%20we%20thought%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Hum%20bhi%20kar%20sakte%20hai%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(we%20can%20do%20it%20too).%20So%20in%202013%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20of%20fa