20hand%20at%20it%20too%20and%20used%20bottles%20at%20home%20to%20make%20a%20few%20lamps%20and%20glass%20jars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20decided%20to%20post%20them%20on%20Facebook.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20an%20overwhelming%20response.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20we%20also%20got%20an%20exhibition%20invite%20from%20The%20Times%20of%20India%20in%20Hyderabad.%20We%20sold%20out%20all%20the%20pieces%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gave%20Madhuri%20and%20Amit%20the%20push%20that%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUpcycling%20bottles%20into%20functional%20art%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20decided%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20dedicate%20themselves%20to%20their%20venture.%20They%20started%20%E2%80%98Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%E2%80%99%20in%202013%2C%20and%20have%20converted%20over%20seven%20lakh%20glass%20bottles%20into%20pieces%20of%20home%20utility%20and%20decor%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20had%20sustainability%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20project%2C%20we%20also%20wanted%20to%20earn%20money%20so%20we%20could%20pay%20off%20the%20rag%20pickers%20and%20other%20employees.%20So%20we%20started%20to%20host%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274565%2Flibrarian-grows-vegetable-fruits-flowers-on-terrace-gardening-facebook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20Facebook%20campaigns%3C%2Fa%3E%20urging%20people%20to%20come%20join%20us%20with%20their%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20advertised%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20caught%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20%E2%80%94%20we%20asked%20them%20to%20come%20with%20their%20bottles%20and%20that%20we%20would%20convert%20the%20bottles%20into%20whatever%20piece%20they%20fancied.%20This%20gave%20a%20boost%20to%20our%20business%2C%20and%20by%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20we%20started%20getting%20flooded%20with%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20sh