ly%20so%20the%20products%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20upcycled%2C%20but%20rather%20feel%20brand%20new!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20social%20media%20campaigns%20also%20resulted%20in%20something%20very%20sweet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20came%20to%20us%20with%20their%20bottles%2C%20many%20shared%20special%20stories%20behind%20each%20of%20them!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20people%20saying%20things%20like%20%E2%80%98I%20opened%20this%20bottle%20when%20my%20daughter%20was%20born%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98My%20best%20friend%20gifted%20me%20this%20bottle%2020%20years%20ago%E2%80%99.%20They%20come%20to%20us%20with%20requests%20to%20save%20the%20bottles%20and%20preserve%20them%20in%20a%20memorable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhuri%20and%20Amit%20share%20that%20such%20requests%20and%20stories%20make%20their%20jobs%20even%20more%20special%20and%20add%20an%20element%20of%20challenge%20to%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20journey%20from%20waste%20to%20wonder%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20the%20process%20of%20upcycling%20starts%2C%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20ways%20in%20which%20we%20collect%20bottles.%20First%2C%20through%20our%20BYOB%20(bring%20your%20own%20bottle)%20initiative%2C%20we%20transform%20the%20bottles%20that%20people%20bring%20to%20us%20into%20whatever%20they%20request%20them%20to%20be.%20Second%2C%20we%20collaborate%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300446%2Ffriends-help-ragpickers-in-kolkata-slum-launch-sustainable-children-fashion-brand-khudey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20with%20rag%20pickers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20collect%20and%20bring%20bottles%20to%20us%2C%20for%20which%20we%20pay%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20and%20Madhuri%20have%20a%20network%20of%20more%20than%20150%20ragpickers%20in%20and%20around%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C