3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pandemic%20significantly%20boosted%20the%20sustainability%20movement.%20Previously%2C%20people%20viewed%20products%20as%20mere%20consumables%20and%20were%20hesitant%20to%20invest%20in%20them.%20However%2C%20the%20situation%20has%20completely%20transformed.%20People%20are%20now%20eager%20to%20make%20extra%20efforts%20to%20avoid%20contributing%20to%20global%20warming%20and%20carbon%20emissions.%20This%20presents%20an%20opportune%20moment%20for%20new%20businesses%20to%20emerge%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20been%20in%20this%20business%20for%20almost%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20duo%20now%20have%20customers%20from%20all%20across%20the%20country%20and%20abroad.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20strong%20customer%20base%20of%20over%2080%2C000%20people%20from%20India%20as%20well%20as%20Canada%2C%20Netherlands%2C%20Dubai%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20our%20project%2C%20we%20want%20to%20give%20people%20an%20alternative%20and%20an%20opportunity%20to%20live%20sustainably.%20This%20project%20is%20beyond%20just%20business%20for%20us%20as%20this%20is%20for%20the%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Madhuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20send%20them%20your%20glass%20bottles%2C%20contact%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkavipoetryart%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691155506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326377%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Noida-based%20Madhuri%20Balodi%20and%20Amit%20Singh%20started%20%E2%80%98Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%E2%80%99%20to%20